(179, 'Railway Station', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'HD-wallpaper-chiasso-train-yard-switzerland-train-europe-red-chiasso-yard-railway-switzerland.jpg', '56', 'A significant crossing point between Switzerland and Italy is the railway station at Chiasso. It has historical significance in the transportation network of the region and is important for cross-border transit.\r\n', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'HD-wallpaper-chiasso-train-yard-switzerland-train-europe-red-chiasso-yard-railway-switzerland.jpg', 'dfsdf'),
(180, 'Museo d\'Arte', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'museum-g4cb0d727b_1920_1675942305694_1675942310765_1675942310765.avif', '56', 'One of the town\'s cultural highlights is the Chiasso Art Museum, which holds a variety of exhibitions. It regularly includes pieces by regional artists in addition to showcasing modern art.\r\n', '', '', '1', '1', '1', 'museum-g4cb0d727b_1920_1675942305694_1675942310765_1675942310765.avif', 'dfsdf'),
(181, 'Duomo (Cathedral of Santa Maria del Fiore)', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'cathedral-of-santa-maria-del-fiore.jpg', '57', 'Florence Cathedral, formally the Cathedral of Saint Mary of the Flower, is the cathedral of Florence, Italy. ', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'cathedral-of-santa-maria-del-fiore.jpg', 'dfsdf'),
(182, 'Uffizi Gallery', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'Uffizi-Gallery-Florence.jpg', '57', 'The Uffizi Gallery is a prominent art museum located adjacent to the Piazza della Signoria in the Historic Centre of Florence in the region of Tuscany, Italy.', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'Uffizi-Gallery-Florence.jpg', 'dfsdf'),
(183, 'Colosseum ', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'Colosseum-Rome-Italy.webp', '58', 'The Colosseum is an elliptical amphitheatre in the centre of the city of Rome, Italy, just east of the Roman Forum.', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'Colosseum-Rome-Italy.webp', 'dfsdf'),
(184, 'Roman Forum', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'buildings-Rome-Roman-Forum.webp', '58', 'The Roman Forum, also known by its Latin name Forum Romanum, is a rectangular forum surrounded by the ruins of several important ancient government buildings at the centre of the city of Rome.', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'buildings-Rome-Roman-Forum.webp', 'dfsdf'),
(185, 'Trevi Fountain', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'trevi-fountain-rome-italy-TREVI0217-4b6f7385c7f0436ba3d5fa2c061a1791.jpg', '58', 'One of Rome\'s earliest water sources is the Trevi Fountain. The fountain was once used to supply water to Rome\'s great fountains and Roman baths. It was built during the Roman era.\r\n', '', '', '1', '1', '1', 'trevi-fountain-rome-italy-TREVI0217-4b6f7385c7f0436ba3d5fa2c061a1791.jpg', 'dfsdf'),
(186, 'Buckingham ', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'Buckingham-Palace-Queen-Victoria-Memorial-London-statue (1).webp', '59', 'Buckingham Palace is a royal residence in London, and the administrative headquarters of the monarch of the United Kingdom. ', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'Buckingham-Palace-Queen-Victoria-Memorial-London-statue (1).webp', 'dfsdf'),
(187, 'The British Museum', '1', 'harshit gupta', '1284244-_x500-nocrop.jpg', '59', 'The British Museum is a public museum dedicated to human history, art and culture located in the Bloomsbury area of London. ', '', '', '1', '1', '12', '1284244-_x500-nocrop.jpg', 'dfsdf'),
(188, 'Pattaya Floating Market', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'Pattaya Floating Market.jpg', '40', 'Pattaya Floating Market is a new tourist destination for Thai cultural conservation located in the heart of Pattaya city. It was established by the owner\'s determination to make the place the center of tourism for cultural conservation that simulates the simple way of life of Thai people. ', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'Pattaya Floating Market.jpg', 'dfsdf'),
(189, 'Jomtien Beach', '1', 'harshit gupta', '5de4ba81e6d33.jpg', '40', 'Jomtien or Jomtien Beach is a town on the east coast of the Gulf of Thailand about 165 km south-east of Bangkok in Chonburi Province.', '', '', '1', '1', '12', '5de4ba81e6d33.jpg', 'dfsdf'),
(190, 'Hulhumale Island', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'Hulhumale-island.avif', '60', 'A man-made island attached to MalÃ© that has parks, beaches, and a calmer vibe than the busy capital.\r\n', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'Hulhumale-island.avif', 'dfsdf'),
(191, 'MalÃ© Friday Mosque', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'Friday-mosque-1024x768.jpg', '60', 'The MalÃ© Friday Mosque or the MalÃ© Hukuru Miskiy also known as the Old Friday Mosque is one of the oldest and most ornate mosques in the city of MalÃ©, Kaafu Atoll, Maldives.', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'Friday-mosque-1024x768.jpg', 'dfsdf'),
(192, 'Republic Square (Jumhooree Maidhaan)', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'place-2014-08-06-15-Republicsquare6ddaac0df7dd2a75a0e8b8f075c3d1fd.jpg', '60', 'Jumhooree Maidhaan, also known as Independence Square and Republic Square, is an unforgettable sight, especially for visitors who arrive to Male via the sea. ', '', '', '1', '1', '1', 'place-2014-08-06-15-Republicsquare6ddaac0df7dd2a75a0e8b8f075c3d1fd.jpg', 'dfsdf'),
(193, 'Sky Tower', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'c4.jpg', '61', 'The Sky Tower is one of Auckland\'s most iconic landmarks and a must-visit attraction. ', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'c4.jpg', 'dfsdf'),
(194, 'Auckland War Memorial Museum', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'auckland_war_memorial_jxM5qMw.jpg', '61', 'The Auckland War Memorial Museum, also known simply as the Auckland Museum, is one of New Zealand\'s most important and iconic cultural institutions.', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'auckland_war_memorial_jxM5qMw.jpg', 'dfsdf'),
(195, 'Queen Street', '1', 'harshit gupta', '4MBYL2H_image_crop_120892.webp', '61', 'Queen Street is one of Auckland\'s most important and bustling thoroughfares, serving as the main commercial and retail artery of the city.', '', '', '1', '1', '12', '4MBYL2H_image_crop_120892.webp', 'dfsdf'),
(196, 'Te Papa Tongarewa (Museum of New Zealand)', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'Museum_of_New_Zealand_Te_Papa_Tongarewa.jpg', '62', 'The Museum of New Zealand Te Papa Tongarewa is New Zealand\'s national museum and is located in Wellington.', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'Museum_of_New_Zealand_Te_Papa_Tongarewa.jpg', 'dfsdf'),
(197, 'Wellington Cable Car and Botanic Garden', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'img-1713982452-2474-3078085-tbd-asset__aWxvdmVrZWxseQo_CropResizeWzE5MDAsMTAwMCw3NSwianBnIl0.jpg', '62', 'Enjoy easy access to the Botanic Garden, Cable Car Museum, Space Place (at Carter Observatory) and Zealandia (via free shuttle). ', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'img-1713982452-2474-3078085-tbd-asset__aWxvdmVrZWxseQo_CropResizeWzE5MDAsMTAwMCw3NSwianBnIl0.jpg', 'dfsdf'),
(198, 'Weta Workshop', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'weta-workshop-unleashed-bigature-castle.jpg', '62', 'WÄ“tÄ Workshop is a special effects and prop company as well as video game developer based in Miramar, Wellington, in New Zealand, that produces effects for television and film.', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'weta-workshop-unleashed-bigature-castle.jpg', 'dfsdf'),
(199, 'Canterbury Museum', '1', 'harshit gupta', '20-02_CM-East-Facade-Viewed-From-Rolleston-Ave-1500.webp', '63', 'The Canterbury Museum is a museum located in the central city of Christchurch, New Zealand, in the city\'s Cultural Precinct.', '', '', '1', '1', '12', '20-02_CM-East-Facade-Viewed-From-Rolleston-Ave-1500.webp', 'dfsdf'),
(200, 'Christchurch Cathedral', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'Christchurch-Cathedral-Christchurch.png', '63', 'ChristChurch Cathedral, also called Christ Church Cathedral and Cathedral Church of Christ, is a deconsecrated Anglican cathedral in the city of Christchurch, New Zealand. ', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'Christchurch-Cathedral-Christchurch.png', 'dfsdf'),
(201, 'Punting on the Avon', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'img-1713699076-5798-1612399-tbd-asset__aWxvdmVrZWxseQo_CropResizeWzk0MCw1MzAsOTAsImpwZyJd.jpg', '63', 'Enjoy a traditional punt ride along the Avon River, offering scenic views of the city\'s gardens and historic buildings.', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'img-1713699076-5798-1612399-tbd-asset__aWxvdmVrZWxseQo_CropResizeWzk0MCw1MzAsOTAsImpwZyJd.jpg', 'dfsdf'),
(202, 'Monteith\'s Brewery', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'b2.jpg', '64', 'Renowned for its artisan beers and guided brewery tours, this is one of the most well-known breweries in New Zealand.\r\n', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'b2.jpg', 'sd'),
(203, 'Shantytown Heritage Park', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'China-Town-West-Coast.webp', '64', 'A recreated 19th-century gold-mining town, offering a glimpse into New Zealand\'s pioneering past', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'China-Town-West-Coast.webp', 'dfsdf'),
(204, 'Lake Wakatipu', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'Queenstown-from-Bobs-Peak3.jpg', '65', 'Lake Wakatipu is an inland lake in the South Island of New Zealand. It is in the southwest corner of the Otago region, near its boundary with Southland.', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'Queenstown-from-Bobs-Peak3.jpg', 'dfsdf'),
(205, 'Skyline Queenstown', '1', 'harshit gupta', '12-min-2.webp', '65', 'A must-visit attraction accessed via gondola, offering panoramic views of Queenstown, Lake Wakatipu, and the Remarkables.', '', '', '1', '1', '12', '12-min-2.webp', 'dfsdf'),
(206, 'Arrowtown', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'photo-1589445554431-433b6912ca44.jfif', '65', 'Arrowtown is a historic gold mining town in the Otago region of the South Island of New Zealand.', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'photo-1589445554431-433b6912ca44.jfif', 'dfsdf'),
(207, 'Sentosa Island', '1', 'Shiv', 'Sentosa Island.jpg', '44', 'Popular resort location Sentosa Island in Singapore is well-known for its beaches, opulent hotels, and attractions including Universal Studios Singapore. It is a popular destination for travellers since it provides a variety of relaxation, adventure, and entertainment opportunities.', 'Universal Studios Singapore, S.E.A. Aquarium, Sentosa Beaches', '', '1', '1', '10000', 'Sentosa Island3.jpg,Sentosa Island2.jpg,Sentosa Island1.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3988.8719694833367!2d103.82598887403492!3d1.2479458618968702!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31da1f4a6f8857a1%3A0x6a0f1542bf17a7a9!2sSentosa%20Island!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v17200698238'),
(208, 'Chinatown', '1', 'Shiv', 'Chinatown.jpg', '44', 'Singapore\'s Chinatown is a thriving cultural zone famous for its ancient temples, street markets, and rich history. If you want to see traditional Chinese culture amongst futuristic skyscrapers, you have to go there.', 'Chinatown, Buddha Tooth Relic Temple, Chinatown Heritage Centre', '', '1', '1', '10000', 'Chinatown3.jpg,Chinatown2.jpg,Chinatown1.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d7977.643852839377!2d103.8400245874444!3d1.280517871030196!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31da1972a27568e3%3A0xbbc2a66a543ebb05!2sChinatown%2C%20Singapore!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v172007'),
(209, 'Swayambhunath (Monkey Temple)', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'Kathmandu-Swambhuinath.jpg', '66', 'A UNESCO World Heritage Site, this historic temple complex perches on a hill offering sweeping views of the Kathmandu Valley. It is renowned for both the quantity and size of its stupas.\r\n', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'Kathmandu-Swambhuinath.jpg', 'dfsdf'),
(210, 'Pashupatinath Temple', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'pashupatinath-viewpoint.png', '66', 'This temple situated on the banks of the River Bagmati is the most revered Hindu temple in Nepal. The most important festival observed here is Shivaratri.\r\n', '', '', '1', '1', '1', 'pashupatinath-viewpoint.png', 'dfsdf'),
(211, 'Boudhanath Stupa', '1', 'harshit gupta', '1591753869737.jfif', '66', 'one of the biggest stupas in the world and a significant Buddhist pilgrimage site. The stupa\'s surroundings are teeming with Tibetan merchants, monasteries, and cultural events.\r\n', '', '', '1', '1', '12', '1591753869737.jfif', 'dfsdf'),
(212, 'Phewa Lake (Fewa Lake)', '1', 'harshit gupta', '636d08219c7e80680e0a5ffejpeg.jpg', '67', 'The lake that is the second largest in Nepal is the perfect spot for boating, fishing, and relaxing by the water. In addition, the lake offers stunning views of the Annapurna range.', '', '', '1', '1', '12', '636d08219c7e80680e0a5ffejpeg.jpg', 'dfsdf'),
(213, 'Paro Town', '1', 'Shiv', 'paroTown.jpg', '69', 'Bhutan\'s Paro town is a little community known for its colourful markets, traditional architecture, and location as the starting point for the well-known Paro Taktsang monastery, all of which are surrounded by beautiful mountains.', 'Paro Taktsang (Tiger\'s Nest), Rinpung Dzong, National Museum of Bhutan, Kyichu Lhakhang, Drukgyel Dzong', '', '1', '1', '10000', 'paroTown4.jpg,paroTown3.jpg,paroTown2.jpg,paroTown1.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d113351.33433685653!2d89.35484864077368!3d27.399778153175742!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x39e19de85a6c39b7%3A0x1fa780f5a070190!2sParo%2C%20Bhutan!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1720078153901'),
(214, 'Sarangkot', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'Sarangkot.jpg', '67', 'Sarangkot A popular spot for sunrise and sunset views over the Himalayas. It\'s also a famous location for paragliding.', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'Sarangkot.jpg', 'dfsdf'),
(215, 'Gupteshwor Mahadev Cave', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'Gupteshwar-Mahadev-Cave-3.jpg', '67', 'Gupteshwor Mahadev Cave is a cave located in Pokhara-17, Chhorepatan, Kaski district, opposite to Davis Fall, the water from Davis fall passes through this cave.', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'Gupteshwar-Mahadev-Cave-3.jpg', 'dfsdf'),
(216, 'Drukgyel Dzong Area', '1', 'Shiv', 'Drukgyel Dzong Area.jpg', '69', 'With access to hiking paths and beautiful views of Mount Jomolhari, this property is close to the Drukgyel Dzong ruins.', 'Drukgyel Dzong Ruins, Kyichu Lhakhang, Paro Valley Views', '', '1', '1', '10000', 'Drukgyel Dzong Area3.jpg,Drukgyel Dzong Area2.jpg,Drukgyel Dzong Area1.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d14155.603843200606!2d89.30996414028031!3d27.50345540352882!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x39e1737f076a15f5%3A0x136d33899c58c56a!2sDrukgyel%20Dzong%2C%20Bhutan!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1'),
(217, 'Jeep Safari', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'istockphoto-939160216-612x612.jpg', '68', 'Discover the park\'s varied vegetation and wildlife, which includes the Bengal tiger, deer, endangered one-horned rhinoceros, and other bird species.\r\n', '', '', '1', '1', '1', 'istockphoto-939160216-612x612.jpg', 'dfsdf'),
(218, 'Elephant Safari', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'elephant-trekking-shutterstock.jpg', '68', 'See the wildlife up close by taking a ride through the forest on the back of an elephant.', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'elephant-trekking-shutterstock.jpg', 'dfsdf'),
(219, 'Canoe Ride on the Rapti River', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'Canoe Ride on the Rapti River.jpg', '68', 'One of the largest stupas in the world and a significant pilgrimage site for Buddhists.', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'Canoe Ride on the Rapti River.jpg', 'dfsdf'),
(220, 'Bird Watching', '1', 'harshit gupta', 'bird-watching-banner0.jpg', '68', 'With more than 500 different species of birds, Chitwan is a birdwatcher\'s delight. Tours for bird watching in the early morning are highly recommended.\r\n', '', '', '1', '1', '12', 'bird-watching-banner0.jpg', 'dfsdf');
