(221, 'Thimphu City', '1', 'Shiv', 'thimphu.jpg', '70', 'Bhutan\'s capital and primary metropolitan area, with markets, government buildings, and historical sites', 'Tashichho Dzong, Buddha Dordenma, National Memorial Chorten, Changangkha Lhakhang, Folk Heritage Museum', '', '1', '1', '10000', 'thimphu5.jpg,thimphu4.jpg,thimphu3.jpg,thimphu2.jpg,thimphu1.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d113271.10286905697!2d89.56407934398509!3d27.47791399880082!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x39e19419962037b7%3A0x7c01ffe2660560d1!2sThimphu%2C%20Bhutan!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1720081410'),
(222, 'Dechencholing', '1', 'Shiv', 'Dechencholing.jpg', '70', 'A neighbourhood northwest of Thimphu noted for its lovely surroundings and royal homes.', 'Dechencholing Palace,Dechen Phodrang Monastery, Dechencholing Craft Village', '', '1', '1', '10000', 'Dechencholing3.jpg,Dechencholing2.jpg,Dechencholing1.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3537.936215517988!2d89.63567817323263!3d27.53344068074376!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x39e1954127a1033b%3A0x61bb17ce8179e230!2sDechencholing!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1720082149855!5m2'),
(223, 'Punakha Town', '1', 'Shiv', 'punakhaTown.jpg', '75', 'The Punakha district\'s capital and administrative hub, Punakha Dzong and its picturesque environs are its main draws.', 'Punakha Dzong, Chimi Lhakhang, Sangchhen Dorji Lhuendrup Lhakhang Nunnery, Punakha Suspension Bridge, Khamsum Yulley Namgyal Chorten', '', '1', '1', '10000', 'punakhaTown5.jpg,punakhaTown4.jpg,punakhaTown3.jpg,punakhaTown2.jpg,punakhaTown1.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3536.046380801591!2d89.87717097453121!3d27.592091630567076!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x39e1dd0060d8dd2f%3A0x85b0720c2982e58f!2sKhuruthang%20Town!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v172008757405'),
(224, 'Wangdue Phodrang', '1', 'Shiv', 'Wangdue Phodrang.jpg', '75', 'Frequently regarded as a component of the Punakha region, Wangdue Phodrang town is renowned for its dzong and lively indigenous customs.', 'Wangdue Phodrang Dzong, Gangtey Monastery (Gangtey Goenpa), Phobjikha Valley, Jigme Singye Wangchuck National Park, Bajo Town', '', '1', '1', '10000', 'Wangdue Phodrang5.jpg,Wangdue Phodrang4.jpg,Wangdue Phodrang3.jpg,Wangdue Phodrang2.jpg,Wangdue Phodrang1.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d28315.471886073232!2d89.87850622622938!3d27.486875505261313!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x39e1e6ee5b5d65f7%3A0x68c8b38bed7d7a81!2sWangdue%20Phodrang%2C%20Bhutan!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!'),
(225, 'Acropolis of Athens', '1', 'Shiv', 'Acropolis of Athens.jpg', '76', 'Nestled atop a rocky outcrop, the Acropolis in Athens is home to iconic masterpieces like the Parthenon, which stand as testament to the architectural and cultural prowess of ancient Greek culture. It still serves as a symbol of democracy and traditional values and provides expansive vistas of Athens.', 'Parthenon, Erechtheion, Propylaea, Temple of Athena Nike, Odeon of Herodes Atticus, Acropolis Museum, Areopagus Hill', '', '1', '1', '10000', 'Acropolis of Athens6.jpg,Acropolis of Athens5.jpg,Acropolis of Athens4.jpg,Acropolis of Athens3.jpg,Acropolis of Athens2.jpg,Acropolis of Athens1.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3145.2396369055396!2d23.723174275014724!3d37.97153650080283!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x14a1bd1837f5acf3%3A0x5c97c042f5eb0df6!2sAcropolis%20of%20Athens!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v17200'),
(226, 'Parthenon', '1', 'Shiv', 'Parthenon.jpg', '76', 'Famous for its elaborate sculptures, Doric architecture, and historical significance as a representation of Athenian culture and power during the Greek Golden Age, the Parthenon is a temple perched atop the Acropolis in Athens.', 'Architectural Design, Historical Significance, Marble Sculptures, Panoramic Views, Cultural Legacy', '', '1', '1', '10000', 'Parthenon5.jpg,Parthenon4.jpg,Parthenon3.jpg,Parthenon2.jpg,Parthenon1.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3145.2397997150365!2d23.724141675014707!3d37.97153270080302!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x14a1bd19ca39ee61%3A0x1b3fa079b878a218!2sParthenon!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1720095579553!5m2!1'),
(227, 'Knossos Palace', '1', 'Shiv', 'Knossos Palace.jpg', '77', 'The biggest Bronze Age landmark, Knossos Palace in Crete is an important part of the Minoan civilization and has elaborate architecture and colourful frescoes. Steeped in legends such as the Minotaur, it is renowned for its intricate design.', 'Throne Room, Central Court, Queenâ€™s Megaron, Grand Staircase, Hall of the Double Axes', '', '1', '1', '10000', 'Knossos Palace5.jpg,Knossos Palace4.jpg,Knossos Palace3.jpg,Knossos Palace2.jpg,Knossos Palace1.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3256.3227447698505!2d25.160206574875907!3d35.297961250934414!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x149a5916dc7b0f35%3A0xd88c9e5b02743f43!2sKnossos%20Palace!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v17200997341'),
