(238, 'Ubud', '1', 'Shiv', 'bali (3).jpg', '78', 'Situated in the centre of Bali, Ubud is well-known for its calm rice paddies, energetic arts scene, and quiet ambience, rendering it an ideal destination for both relaxation and cultural discovery.', 'Sacred Monkey Forest Sanctuary, Ubud Art Market (Pasar Seni Ubud), Ubud Palace (Puri Saren Agung), Tegallalang Rice Terraces, Goa Gajah (Elephant Cave)', '', '1', '1', '10000', 'bali (8).jpg,bali (7).jpg,bali (6).jpg,bali (5).jpg,bali (4).jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d63136.5523898542!2d115.22483938183672!3d-8.496024093967396!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x2dd23d739f22c9c3%3A0x54a38afd6b773d1c!2sUbud%2C%20Gianyar%20Regency%2C%20Bali%2C%20Indones'),
