(1, 'Stunning Tour of Himachal ', 'Manali ,Rohtang,Shimla', '2N Shimla, 1N Rohtang, 1N Solang Valley, 2N Manali,', 1, '1', 7, '6', 21000, 'person', '2024-07-26', 'himachalstuning.jpg', 1, 'With our Enchanting Himachal Tour, get ready to discover the best of Himachal Pradesh. For your trip to Himachal Pradesh, Sky Globals has designed a 7-day itinerary that lets you see the stunning and well-known hill cities of Shimla and Manali. This package also allows you to visit Chandigarh, the first planned city in India, and its well-known attractions. Explore the world through sightseeing, shopping, adventure sports, and more. To ensure a seamless vacation experience, our tour package includes meals, sightseeing tours, accommodations, and transfers. So, for an amazing vacation in Himachal Pradesh, reserve your tour with Sky Globals right away!\r\n\r\nNote: This is only an example of a proposed itinerary, not everything is achievable. We create packages that fit both your needs and your budget.', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Flight', '0', 6, '3', '1', 1, 'Stunning Tour of Himachal10.jpg,Stunning Tour of Himachal9.jpg,Stunning Tour of Himachal8.jpg,Stunning Tour of Himachal7.jpg,Stunning Tour of Himachal6.jpg,Stunning Tour of Himachal5.jpg,Stunning Tour of Himachal4.jpg,Stunning Tour of Himachal3.jpg,Stunning Tour of Himachal2.jpg,Stunning Tour of Himachal1.jpg', '', 'Himachal Tour Packages', 'Description: Explore the beauty of Himachal with our tour packages. Discover the stunning landscapes and rich culture of this enchanting region.'),
(2, 'Fascinating Whole Tour of Himachal Pradesh', 'Chandigarh, Dalhousie,Delhi,Dharamshala,Kufri,Manali ,Rohtang,Shimla', '1N Delhi, 1N Shimla, 1N Kufri, 1N Manali, 1N Rohtang, 2N Dharamshala, 2N Dalhousie, 1N Chandigarh', 1, '1', 11, '10', 37000, 'person', '2024-07-26', 'himachal1.jpg', 1, 'The captivating state of Himachal Pradesh is home to several incredibly captivating hill stations that draw an absurd amount of tourists each year. With its Whole Tour of Himachal Package, Sky Globals offers you visits to some of the most well-known hill towns in Himachal Pradesh, such as Dalhousie, Dharamshala, Manali, and Shimla. You spend 10 nights and 11 days touring Kufri, Rohtang Pass, and other well-known tourist destinations in the area on this painstakingly designed itinerary. Enjoy the breathtaking scenery that is all around you, have fun, eat a ton of delicious local cuisine, take advantage of the fantastic weather, and more.', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '', '', 1, 'Fascinating Whole Tour of Himachal Pradesh9.jpg,Fascinating Whole Tour of Himachal Pradesh8.jpg,Fascinating Whole Tour of Himachal Pradesh7.jpg,Fascinating Whole Tour of Himachal Pradesh6.jpg,Fascinating Whole Tour of Himachal Pradesh5.jpg,Fascinating Whole Tour of Himachal Pradesh4.jpg,Fascinating Whole Tour of Himachal Pradesh3.jpg,Fascinating Whole Tour of Himachal Pradesh2.jpg,Fascinating Whole Tour of Himachal Pradesh1.jpg,Fascinating Whole Tour of Himachal Pradesh10.jpg', '', 'Himachal Tour Packages', 'Description: Explore the beauty of Himachal with our tour packages. Discover the stunning landscapes and rich culture of this enchanting region.'),
(3, 'A Captivating Tour of Himachal', 'Chandigarh,Chail,Dharamshala,Manali ,Nalagarh ,Palampur,Shimla', '1N Chandigarh, 2N Shimla, 1N Chail, 2N Dharamshala, 1N Palampur, 2N Manali', 1, '1', 10, '9', 32800, 'person', '2024-07-26', 'A Captivating Tour of Himachal8.jpg', 1, 'With our 10-day Himachal tour, you can discover the stunning scenery and vibrant culture of the Himalayan region. You will have a profound understanding of the traditional legacy from this journey. You will see popular tourist destinations like Kali Ka Tibba and Chail Wildlife Sanctuary while on this tour. Adventure seekers would love the Himachal vacation because it offers hiking and skiing at Kufri. Proceed to Solang Nallah, which is well-known for adventure sports like paragliding, zorbing, rock climbing, and rappelling. You will have the chance to visit the world\'s highest cricket ground, Chail Cricket Ground, as part of the 9 nights, 10 days Himachal package. See the Himachal trip package itinerary below for additional information.\r\n', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'A Captivating Tour of Himachal10.jpg,A Captivating Tour of Himachal9.jpg,A Captivating Tour of Himachal8.jpg,A Captivating Tour of Himachal7.jpg,A Captivating Tour of Himachal6.jpg,A Captivating Tour of Himachal5.jpg,A Captivating Tour of Himachal4.jpg,A Captivating Tour of Himachal3.jpg,A Captivating Tour of Himachal2.jpg,A Captivating Tour of Himachal1.jpg', '', 'Himachal Tour Packages', 'Description: Explore the beauty of Himachal with our tour packages. Discover the stunning landscapes and rich culture of this enchanting region.'),
(4, 'Himachal Honeymoon Package', 'Chandigarh,Chail,Kullu,Manali ,Shimla', '1N Chandigarh, 1N Manali, 2N Kullu, 2N Shimla', 1, '1', 7, '6', 26000, 'person', '2024-07-26', 'himachalhoneymoon.jpg', 1, 'This carefully designed itinerary from Sky GlobalsÂ offers you the chance to begin your married life together: the Himachal Honeymoon vacation package. Enjoy a romantic and leisurely experience as you travel through the snow-capped mountain ranges, the unspoiled beauty of nature, and the enormous verdant forests. The \"Honeymooner\'s Paradise,\" as Himachal is sometimes called, offers some of the most beautiful scenery for romantic getaways. The joy of witnessing the hill station\'s tranquility is yours with our Himachal honeymoon vacation package. Shimla, Manali, and Chandigarh are all lovely places to visit while on your honeymoon in Himachal.\r\n', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'Himachal Honeymoon Package10.jpg,Himachal Honeymoon Package9.jpg,Himachal Honeymoon Package8.jpg,Himachal Honeymoon Package7.jpg,Himachal Honeymoon Package6.jpg,Himachal Honeymoon Package5.jpg,Himachal Honeymoon Package4.jpg,Himachal Honeymoon Package3.jpg,Himachal Honeymoon Package2.jpg,Himachal Honeymoon Package1.jpg', '', 'Himachal Tour Packages', 'Description: Explore the beauty of Himachal with our tour packages. Discover the stunning landscapes and rich culture of this enchanting region.'),
(5, 'Himachal Trip With Amritsar', 'Amritsar,Chandigarh,Delhi,Dharamshala,Manali ,Shimla', '2N Amritsar, 2N Chandigarh, 2N Delhi, 3N Dharamshala, 2N Manali', 1, '1', 12, '11', 35300, 'person', '2024-07-26', 'amritsar2.jpg', 1, 'Take advantage of Amritsar\'s amazing Himachal Pradesh tour to make every time unforgettable. If you want to see the best of this Indian state, the 11-night, 12-day Himachal Fantasy Tour is a great choice. You will go to the hill towns of Dharamshala, Manali, and Shimla as well as Chandigarh and Delhi during your Himachal trip. The schedule includes adventure activities at well-known locations such as Kufri, Solang Valley, and Rohtang Pass. Meals, lodging, transportation, and sightseeing are all included in our travel package. To learn more about this Himachal with Amritsar travel itinerary, view the itinerary below.\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'Himachal Trip With Amritsar10.jpg,Himachal Trip With Amritsar9.jpg,Himachal Trip With Amritsar8.jpg,Himachal Trip With Amritsar7.jpg,Himachal Trip With Amritsar6.jpg,Himachal Trip With Amritsar5.jpg,Himachal Trip With Amritsar4.jpg,Himachal Trip With Amritsar3.jpg,Himachal Trip With Amritsar2.jpg,Himachal Trip With Amritsar1.jpg', '', 'Himachal Tour Packages', 'Description: Explore the beauty of Himachal with our tour packages. Discover the stunning landscapes and rich culture of this enchanting region.'),
(6, 'Tour of himachal', 'Dharamshala,Manali ,Shimla', '2N Dharamshala, 2N Manali', 1, '1', 5, '4', 25999, 'person', '2024-07-26', 'manali (2).jpg', 1, 'Enjoy an incredible tour of Himachal Pradesh with Sky Globals to make your every moment remarkable. The 4-night, 5-day Himachal Fantasy Tour will be a perfect option if you want to explore the best of this Indian state in a short time. During the Himachal trip, you will visit the hill towns of Shimla, Manali, and Dharamshala. Check out the itinerary below to know more about this Himachal tour itinerary with Sky Globals, covering Shimla, Manali, and Dharamshala.', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'Tour of himachal10.jpg,Tour of himachal9.jpg,Tour of himachal8.jpg,Tour of himachal7.jpg,Tour of himachal5.jpg,Tour of himachal4.jpg,Tour of himachal3.jpg,Tour of himachal2.jpg,Tour of himachal1.jpg,Tour of himachal6.jpg', '', 'Himachal Tour Packages', 'Description: Explore the beauty of Himachal with our tour packages. Discover the stunning landscapes and rich culture of this enchanting region.'),
(7, 'Tour of Vaishno Devi ', ' Gulmarg,Jammu ,Katra ,Pahalgam,Srinagar', '1N Jammu, 1N Katra, 1N Pahalga, 1N Srinagar, 2N Gulmarg ', 1, '2', 7, '6', 18000, 'person', '2024-07-26', 'katra1.jpg', 2, 'The state of Jammu & Kashmir in northern India is the perfect place to spend an amazing holiday with your loved ones. With the Kashmir with Vaishno Devi tour from Sky GlobalsÂ you may honor the most venerated Mata Vaishno Devi shrine and explore some of the most well-known locations in Kashmirâ€”dubbed \"Heaven on Earth.\" Enjoy darshan at the Vaishno Devi cave temple and engage in sightseeing and other leisure activities in charming locations like as Srinagar, Pahalgam, Sonamarg, and Gulmarg when on the Kashmir with Vaishno Devi itinerary. Visit the Mughal Gardens and have a Shikara ride in Dal Lake.Sky GlobalsÂ guarantees a stress-free experience with things like cozy accommodations, smooth transfers, and our knowledgeable guides who are knowledgeable about the history and culture of the area.', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'Tour of Vaishno Devi10.jpg,Tour of Vaishno Devi9.jpg,Tour of Vaishno Devi8.jpg,Tour of Vaishno Devi7.jpg,Tour of Vaishno Devi6.jpg,Tour of Vaishno Devi5.jpg,Tour of Vaishno Devi4.jpg,Tour of Vaishno Devi3.jpg,Tour of Vaishno Devi2.jpg,Tour of Vaishno Devi1.jpg', '', 'Kashmir Tour Packages', 'Description: Plan your dream vacation to Kashmir with our customizable tour packages. Immerse yourself in the natural beauty and warm hospitality of the region.'),
(8, 'Unique Kashmir Tour For 7-Day\'s', ' Gulmarg,Pahalgam,Srinagar,Sonamarg ', '2N Pahalgam, 2N Srinagar, 1N Gulmarg, 1N Sonamarg ', 1, '2', 7, '6', 18289, 'person', '2024-07-26', 'Unique Kashmir Tour For 7-Days7.jpg', 2, 'It is accurate to refer to Kashmir in India as a \"heaven on earth.\" Choose the Unique Kashmir TourÂ if you wish to see some of this Indian state\'s most breathtaking locations. You may visit locations like Srinagar, Gulmarg, Pahalgam, and Sonamarg in seven days. You will love enjoying a Shikara ride on Dal Lake, staying on a houseboat, and touring the well-known tourist attractions while on the tour. To ensure a seamless vacation experience, our tour package includes meals, sightseeing tours, accommodations, and transfers. So, reserve your trip with Sky GlobalsÂ right away for an amazing vacation to Kashmir!\r\n\r\nNote: This is only an example of a proposed itinerary, not everything is achievable. We create packages that fit both your needs and your budget. If you would like changes made, get in touch with our trip experts.', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'Unique Kashmir Tour For 7-Days10.jpg,Unique Kashmir Tour For 7-Days9.jpg,Unique Kashmir Tour For 7-Days8.jpg,Unique Kashmir Tour For 7-Days7.jpg,Unique Kashmir Tour For 7-Days6.jpg,Unique Kashmir Tour For 7-Days5.jpg,Unique Kashmir Tour For 7-Days4.jpg,Unique Kashmir Tour For 7-Days3.jpg,Unique Kashmir Tour For 7-Days2.jpg,Unique Kashmir Tour For 7-Days1.jpg', '', 'Kashmir Tour Packages', 'Description: Plan your dream vacation to Kashmir with our customizable tour packages. Immerse yourself in the natural beauty and warm hospitality of the region.'),
(9, 'Kashmir Honeymoon Package', ' Gulmarg,Pahalgam,Srinagar,Sonamarg ', '1N Pahalgam, 2N Srinagar, 1N Sonamarg, 1N Gulmarg ', 1, '2', 6, '5', 24600, 'person', '2024-07-26', 'kashmirhoneymoon.jpg', 2, 'We offer a once-in-a-lifetime honeymoon package to Kashmir that lasts for five nights and six days. This painstakingly designed Kashmir tour package gives you the chance to discover the amazing beauty of the area. You may engage in a variety of romantic activities, such as a nature walk, a sightseeing tour, a Gondola ride, and a Shikara ride. Additionally, see some of Kashmir\'s most stunning cities, including Pahalgam, Gulmarg, Sonmarg, and Srinagar. For a seamless travel experience, the Kashmir honeymoon package provides cozy lodging, fascinating tours, delectable meals, and quick transportation.\r\n\r\n\r\nNote: You can alter the itinerary to suit your needs and create this Kashmir honeymoon package. Get in touch with us to schedule a tour or for additional information!\r\n', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'Kashmir Honeymoon Package10.jpg,Kashmir Honeymoon Package9.jpg,Kashmir Honeymoon Package8.jpg,Kashmir Honeymoon Package7.jpg,Kashmir Honeymoon Package6.jpg,Kashmir Honeymoon Package5.jpg,Kashmir Honeymoon Package4.jpg,Kashmir Honeymoon Package3.jpg,Kashmir Honeymoon Package2.jpg,Kashmir Honeymoon Package1.jpg', '', 'Kashmir Tour Packages', 'Description: Plan your dream vacation to Kashmir with our customizable tour packages. Immerse yourself in the natural beauty and warm hospitality of the region.'),
(10, 'Amarnath Yatra Tour Package ', ' Gulmarg,Pahalgam,Srinagar,Sonamarg ', '2N Pahalgam, 1N Srinagar, 1N Sonamarg, 1N Gulmarg', 1, '2', 6, '5', 30800, 'person', '2024-07-26', 'amarnath.jpg', 2, 'With our 5-day Amarnath Yatra Package departing from Hyderabad by air, set off on a spiritual pilgrimage. You will receive divine graces on this excursion and be able to appreciate the Kashmir valleys\' unadulterated beauty. Along with relaxing Shikara rides in Dal Lake, the package includes recreational activities like hiking, skiing, and golfing. Our accommodation, transfers, meals, and sightseeing tours are all included in our Amarnath yatra vacation packages from Hyderabad, guaranteeing a hassle-free and easy trip to Kashmir.Â ', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'Amarnath Yatra Tour Package10.jpg,Amarnath Yatra Tour Package9.jpg,Amarnath Yatra Tour Package8.jpg,Amarnath Yatra Tour Package7.jpg,Amarnath Yatra Tour Package6.jpg,Amarnath Yatra Tour Package5.jpg,Amarnath Yatra Tour Package4.jpg,Amarnath Yatra Tour Package3.jpg,Amarnath Yatra Tour Package2.jpg,Amarnath Yatra Tour Package1.jpg', '', 'Kashmir Tour Packages', 'Description: Plan your dream vacation to Kashmir with our customizable tour packages. Immerse yourself in the natural beauty and warm hospitality of the region.'),
(11, 'KASHMIR TOUR', ' Gulmarg,Pahalgam,Srinagar,Sonamarg ', '1N Pahalgam, 2N Srinagar, 1N Sonamarg ', 1, '2', 4, '3', 49999, 'person', '2024-07-29', 'pahalgam1.jpg', 2, 'A fascinating 4-day, 3-night journey to Srinagar, Gulmarg, Pahalgam, and Sonmarg is available with Sky Globals. When you arrive in Srinagar, you\'ll be greeted and taken to your hotel or houseboat to start the tour. Take a leisurely shikara ride on Dal Lake after touring the famous Mughal Gardens, Dal Lake, and Shankaracharya Temple. Travel to Gulmarg the following day, which is well-known for its breathtaking scenery and the Gulmarg Gondola, one of the world\'s tallest cable cars. Following a night spent in Srinagar, the journey proceeds to Pahalgam, also referred to as the \"Valley of Shepherds,\" where you may engage in horseback riding or just take in the breathtaking scenery. Sonmarg, often known as the \"Meadow of Gold,\" is the last stop and is renowned for its breathtaking glaciers and hiking opportunities.', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'KASHMIR TOUR10.jpg,KASHMIR TOUR9.jpg,KASHMIR TOUR8.jpg,KASHMIR TOUR7.jpg,KASHMIR TOUR6.jpg,KASHMIR TOUR5.jpg,KASHMIR TOUR4.jpg,KASHMIR TOUR3.jpg,KASHMIR TOUR2.jpg,KASHMIR TOUR1.jpg', '', 'Kashmir Tour Packages', 'Description: Plan your dream vacation to Kashmir with our customizable tour packages. Immerse yourself in the natural beauty and warm hospitality of the region.'),
(12, 'Trip to Goa For  3 Days ', '', '1N North Goa, 2N South Goa', 1, '3', 3, '2', 5899, 'person', '2024-07-29', 'Trip to Goa For 3 Days1.jpg', 3, 'This three-day schedule in Goa is a great way for travelers to take in the sun, sand, and surf. The Goa three-day package will begin with a visit of the Old Goa churches, including the Chapel of St. Francis Xavier and the Basilica of Bom Jesus, which have been designated by UNESCO as World Heritage Sites.\r\n\r\nAs part of this Goa three-day package, you will later visit well-known North Goa beaches like Anjuna, Baga, and Calangute beach. The last day of your three-day Goa tour is devoted to exploring Colva Beach, a well-known South Goan beach. This three-day Goa itinerary includes easy transfers, comfortable lodging, delectable meals, thrilling water sports, and sightseeing. So, seize this 3-day tour to Goa.', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'Trip to Goa For 3 Days10.jpg,Trip to Goa For 3 Days9.jpg,Trip to Goa For 3 Days8.jpg,Trip to Goa For 3 Days7.jpg,Trip to Goa For 3 Days6.jpg,Trip to Goa For 3 Days5.jpg,Trip to Goa For 3 Days4.jpg,Trip to Goa For 3 Days3.jpg,Trip to Goa For 3 Days2.jpg,Trip to Goa For 3 Days1.jpg', '', 'Goa Tour Packages', 'Description: Plan your perfect getaway with our Goa tour packages, featuring stunning beaches, exciting water sports, and unforgettable cultural experiences.'),
(13, 'Memorable Vacations in Goa', '', '1N North Goa, 1N Old Goa, 1N South Goa', 1, '3', 4, '3', 8500, 'person', '2024-07-29', 'Untitled design (33).png', 3, 'Goa, India\'s premier party destination, is stunning for all the right reasons. People intend to spend a weekend or longer excursions here. Sky Globals. has a fantastic package to offer everyone who wants to spend a few days at this amazing location. With this package, you can spend three nights and four days having fun with your traveling friends. \r\n\r\nWith this package, you can travel to several locations in comfort and not bother about making reservations or making travel arrangements. The package includes lodging, meals, tourist excursions, and a lot more. This package will undoubtedly make your next vacation to Goa unforgettable if you reserve it.', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Flight', '0', 0, '', '', 1, 'southgoa1.jpg,Memorable Vacations in Goa7.jpg,Memorable Vacations in Goa6.jpg,Memorable Vacations in Goa5.jpg,Memorable Vacations in Goa4.jpg,Memorable Vacations in Goa2.jpg,Memorable Vacations in Goa1.jpg,Memorable Vacations in Goa8.jpg,Memorable Vacations in Goa9.jpg,Memorable Vacations in Goa10.jpg', '', 'Goa Tour Packages', 'Description: Plan your perfect getaway with our Goa tour packages, featuring stunning beaches, exciting water sports, and unforgettable cultural experiences.'),
(14, 'Goa\'s Fun-Packed Week', '', '2N North Goa Beaches, 3N  South Goa', 1, '3', 7, '6', 18899, 'person', '2024-07-29', 'Untitled design (34).png', 3, 'Goa makes the most of life. Fantastic beaches and exciting events are held here, and the old buildings serve as a testament to its rich past. With the masterfully designed 7-day Goa Itinerary, you may enjoy some beautiful sightseeing as well as all the tastes that Goa has to offer. You will see Goa\'s beaches, forts, and cathedrals, among other well-known tourist destinations, during this journey. You will also get to see the breathtaking waterfalls, taste the delectable cuisine of this area, and feel the excitement of a variety of water activities. Stated differently, you will be able to take advantage of everything that this location has to offer with this tour.\r\n\r\nNote: This is only a hypothetical itinerary that shows you what might be able to do.', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Flight', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'Goa Fun-Packed Week9.jpg,Goa Fun-Packed Week8.jpg,Goa Fun-Packed Week7.jpg,Goa Fun-Packed Week6.jpg,Goa Fun-Packed Week5.jpg,Goa Fun-Packed Week4.jpg,Goa Fun-Packed Week3.jpg,Goa Fun-Packed Week2.jpg,Goa Fun-Packed Week1.jpg,Goa Fun-Packed Week.jpg', '', 'Goa Tour Packages', 'Description: Plan your perfect getaway with our Goa tour packages, featuring stunning beaches, exciting water sports, and unforgettable cultural experiences.'),
(15, ' Goa Honeymoon Package', '', '1N North Goa, 2N South Goa', 1, '3', 4, '3', 30000, 'couple', '2024-07-29', 'Goa Honeymoon Package.png', 3, 'Without a question, Goa is the most popular honeymoon location for people worldwide. Its gorgeous beaches with smooth golden sands and breathtaking views offer the ideal backdrop for couples hoping to have a fun time on their honeymoon tour in Goa. Goa\'s beaches are divided into two categories: North Goa and South Goa beaches. Still, they differ greatly from one another. While South Goa\'s beaches, like Majorda Beach and Butterfly Beach, are calm and ideal for people looking to spend a relaxing day at the beach, North Goa\'s beaches, like Vagator Beach, Baga Beach, and Anjuna Beach, are well-known for throwing the most amazing parties in the area. ', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '', '', 1, 'Goa Honeymoon Package10.jpg,Goa Honeymoon Package8.jpg,Goa Honeymoon Package7.jpg,Goa Honeymoon Package6.jpg,Goa Honeymoon Package5.jpg,Goa Honeymoon Package4.jpg,Goa Honeymoon Package3.jpg,Goa Honeymoon Package2.jpg,Goa Honeymoon Package1.jpg,Goa Honeymoon Package9.jpg', '', 'Goa Tour Packages', 'Description: Plan your perfect getaway with our Goa tour packages, featuring stunning beaches, exciting water sports, and unforgettable cultural experiences.'),
(16, 'Discover Kerala with Athirapally Waterfall Tour', 'Athirapally,Alappuzha,Kochi,Kovalam,Munnar,Trivandrum', '1N Athirapally, 1N Munnar, 1N Alappuzha, 1N Kovalam, 1N Trivandrum, 2N Kochi', 1, '4', 8, '7', 21899, 'person', '2024-07-29', 'Discover Kerala with Athirapally Waterfall Tour (2).jpg', 4, 'Discover Kerala\'s splendor with our carefully planned Kerala travel itinerary that includes the Athirapally Waterfall. The powerful Athirapally waterfalls and numerous other tourist spots in \"God\'s Own Country\" are included in this tour. You will also cover the main tourist destinations like Thiruvananthapuram, Alleppey, Kovalam, and Munnar.\r\n\r\nYou can enjoy exciting activities like beachside games and Ayurvedic massages when you travel to Athirapally Falls. Additionally, the highlight of this 8-day Kerala Athirapally trip package, which includes meals, lodging, sightseeing tours, and quick transfers, is taking in the picturesque houseboat ride in the backwater.\r\n\r\nNote: This is merely a suggested schedule to show you what this 8-day Kerala vacation package could be able to accomplish. For any changes, get in touch with us.\r\n', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'Discover Kerala with Athirapally Waterfall Tour10.jpg,Discover Kerala with Athirapally Waterfall Tour9.jpg,Discover Kerala with Athirapally Waterfall Tour8.jpg,Discover Kerala with Athirapally Waterfall Tour7.jpg,Discover Kerala with Athirapally Waterfall Tour6.jpg,Discover Kerala with Athirapally Waterfall Tour5.jpg,Discover Kerala with Athirapally Waterfall Tour4.jpg,Discover Kerala with Athirapally Waterfall Tour3.jpg,Discover Kerala with Athirapally Waterfall Tour2.jpg,Discover Kerala with Athirapally Waterfall Tour1.jpg', '', 'Kerala Tour Packages', 'Discover the beauty of Kerala with our exclusive tour packages. Explore the backwaters, beaches, and cultural heritage of this enchanting destination.'),
