(33, 'Badrinath Kedarnath Yatra 2024', 'Badrinath,Guptkashi,Har Ki Pauri, Haridwar,Kedarnath ,Rudraprayag', '1N Haridwar, 1N Guptkashi, 1N Kedarnath, 1N Badrinath, 1N Rudraprayag ', 1, '7', 6, '5', 20600, 'person', '2024-07-29', 'badrinath.jpg', 7, 'Take a six-day trip that will change your life with the Divine Badrinath Kedarnath Yatra. This is a rare chance to visit Kedarnath and Badrinath, the two holiest pilgrimage destinations for Hindus. Both have great spiritual value and are endowed with captivating beauty. You can establish a genuine spiritual connection at Kedarnath, one of Shiva\'s twelve Jyotirlingas, and the Badrinath shrine, one of Lord Vishnu\'s 108 Divya Desams. During the Uttarakhand Do Dham Yatra, you can also visit Guptkashi, Rudraprayag, Haridwar, and Rishikesh with the Badrinath Kedarnath vacation package.\r\n\r\nOur 5-Night/6-Day Badrinath Kedarnath Tour Package, which departs from Haridwar, includes a number of features that guarantee a stress-free vacation, like cozy accommodations, delectable meals, and smooth transfers. So, make your tour now with Sky Globals for a Badrinath Kedarnath Yatra.Â                                    \r\n\r\nNote: This is only an example of a proposed itinerary, not everything is achievable. We create packages that fit both your needs and your budget. If you would want changes made to your vacation, get in touch with our travel specialists and we will work with you to create a memorable Do Dham tour that suits your needs.\r\n', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'guptkashi1.jpg', '', 'Uttarakhand Tour Packages', ''),
