(35, 'Mandawa Trip With Golden Triangle', 'Agra,Delhi,jaipur ,Mandawa ', '1N Delhi, 1N Agra, 2N Jaipur, 2N Mandawa ', 1, '8', 7, '6', 18700, 'person', '2024-07-29', 'goldentrang.jpg', 8, 'Set out on an adventurous tour to discover Mandawa as well as the best of Delhi, Agra, and Jaipur. Select this 7-day Golden Triangle with Mandawa tour to discover amazing destinations that showcase vintage charm, culture, history, and legacy. See the magnificent murals and exquisitely painted havelis at Mandawa in addition to the forts, palaces, and monuments. The magical splendor of the Taj Mahal in Agra will captivate you, and an unforgettable elephant ride in Jaipur is in store for you.\r\n\r\nThroughout the vacation, Sky GlobalsÂ takes care of all of your needs. With the Mandawa package, meals, transportation, lodging, and sightseeing are all suitably included and organized inside the Golden Triangle. ', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'Agra (6).jpg,delhi1.jpg,jaipur (7).jpg', '', 'Delhi Tour Packages', '');
