(36, 'Tour Package for Delhi and Agra', 'Agra,Delhi', '1N Delhi, 2N Agra', 1, '8', 4, '3', 8600, 'person', '2024-07-29', 'delhi (10).jpg', 8, 'Discover the timeless beauty and historical significance of Delhi and Agra like never before by planning an escape. This 4-day tour package from Delhi to Agra is tailored specifically for you. Major tourist destinations in Delhi and Agra, such as India Gate, Raj Ghat, Jama Masjid, Taj Mahal, Red Fort, and Fatehpur Sikri, are included in the itinerary. While you visit these breathtaking architectural marvels, make sure to capture some amazing photos.  Additionally, we provide affordable and economical trip packages from Delhi to Agra. The package includes efficient transportation, sanitary meals, and cozy lodging.\r\n\r\nNote that this is merely a proposed itinerary to give you an idea of what might be feasible. We are able to tailor a four-day Delhi Agra travel package to your individual preferences. \r\n', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '', '', 1, 'agra.jpg,delhi (11).jpg', '', 'Delhi Tour Packages', ''),
(37, '4 - Days Ayodhya And varanasi Tour', 'Ayodhya,Varanasi', '1N Ayodhya, 2N Varanasi, ', 1, '9', 4, '3', 18200, 'person', '2024-07-29', 'ayodhya (8).jpg', 9, 'Sky Global offers an enriching 4-day tour of Ayodhya and Varanasi, perfect for those seeking a spiritual and cultural experience. The journey begins with your arrival in Ayodhya, where you\'ll be greeted and transferred to your hotel. Spend the day exploring the city\'s sacred landmarks, including the Ram Janmabhoomi, Hanuman Garhi, and Kanak Bhawan Temple. On the second day, after a morning in Ayodhya, you\'ll travel to Varanasi, one of the oldest living cities in the world. Check into your Varanasi hotel and enjoy a serene evening boat ride on the Ganges River, witnessing the mesmerizing Ganga Aarti. Day three is dedicated to exploring Varanasi\'s spiritual heritage with visits to the Kashi Vishwanath Temple, Sarnath, and the ancient ghats. The tour concludes on the fourth day with some leisure time in Varanasi before your departure, leaving you with profound memories of these two iconic Indian cities.', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'Varanasi (5).jpg', '', 'Uttar Pradesh Tour Packages', ''),
(38, 'Enchanting Ayodhya Trip', 'Ayodhya', '2N Ayodhya', 1, '9', 3, '2', 14000, 'person', '2024-07-29', 'Ayodhya (6).jpg', 9, 'Sky Global offers an enchanting 3-day trip to Ayodhya, immersing you in the spiritual and historical essence of this revered city. Upon arrival, youâ€™ll be warmly welcomed and transferred to your hotel for a comfortable stay. The journey begins with visits to iconic sites such as the Ram Janmabhoomi, believed to be the birthplace of Lord Rama, and Hanuman Garhi, a significant temple dedicated to Lord Hanuman. The second day is devoted to exploring the serene Ghats of the Sarayu River, where you can experience the tranquil atmosphere and participate in the evening Aarti ceremony. Additional highlights include the Kanak Bhawan, a beautiful temple with intricate architecture, and the Nageshwarnath Temple, known for its religious importance. Throughout the trip, youâ€™ll have ample opportunities to delve into Ayodhyaâ€™s rich cultural heritage, offering a blend of spiritual enlightenment and historical exploration.', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'Ayodhya (5).jpg,Ayodhya (7).jpg', '', 'Uttar Pradesh Tour Packages', ''),
(39, ' Mathura Vrindavan And Agra Tour', 'Agra,Delhi,Mathura,Vrindavan ', '1N Mathura, 2N Agra, ', 1, '9', 4, '3', 8500, 'person', '2024-07-29', 'mathura (5).jpg', 9, 'Explore the historical and sacred sites along the Yamuna River in the Indian state of Uttar Pradesh, located in the north. With the 4 days- 3 night trip, Divine Mathura and Vrindavan with Agra, you may explore the birth location of Lord Krishna, Mathura. There are several temples and locations there that are connected to the life of the Lord. Another place to visit is Vrindavan, a tiny town equally well-known for its religious characteristics. Numerous temples exist that depict the love story between Krishna and Radha. Although Mathura is a popular pilgrimage site, tourists can also find the area to be fascinating. The journey\'s final destination is Agra, which is dotted with the elaborate Mughal artwork. The centerpiece of is the renowned Taj Mahal.', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'Agra (5).jpg,agra.jpg', '', 'Uttar Pradesh Tour Packages', ''),
(40, 'Tour of Spiritual Varanasi', 'Delhi,Varanasi', '1N Delhi, 2N Varanasi, ', 1, '9', 4, '3', 6700, 'person', '2024-07-29', 'Varanasi (5).jpg', 9, 'Visit Varanasi, one of India\'s holiest cities. Even a plunge in the Ganga River, which meanders through Varanasi, is thought to wash away all sins due to the city\'s extreme purity.  The city is referred to as the \"land of moksh\" (liberation from the circle of life).  \r\n\r\n\r\n', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'delhi3.jpg,Varanasi (5).jpg', '', 'Uttar Pradesh Tour Packages', ''),
(41, 'Andaman Trip For 7 Days', 'Havelock Island,Neil Island,Port Blair', '2N Port Blair, 2N Havelock Island, 2N Neil Island, ', 1, '10', 7, '6', 23000, 'person', '2024-07-30', 'Port Blair (8).jpg', 10, 'To properly discover the length and width of the Union Territory of India, Andaman and Nicobar Islands, go with a local vacation expert! This seven-day Andaman itinerary will begin and end in Port Blair and visit Havelock Island and Neil Island. Because this Andaman itinerary was meticulously planned by enthusiastic local Andaman hoppers just like you, you will acquire unforgettable experiences! With Sky Globals, discover adventures that will change your life in the Maldives, Andaman Islands, and Nicobar Island. A tasty lunch twice a day, hassle-free transportation, clean lodging, and flexible sightseeing options are all provided for you! Take a look at the 7-day, condensed Andaman Itinerary to realize your dreams without breaking the bank.\r\n\r\nTravelers should be aware that this itinerary can be customized for a maximum of seven days. You can also choose the date you would want to depart. This sample schedule is designed to provide you with the greatest possible sense of what a 7-day Andaman itinerary could include!\r\n', 'Flights', 'Meals', '0', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'andamanNicobar (3).jpg,andamanNicobar (2).jpg', '', 'Andaman Tour Packages', 'Description: Explore the pristine beauty of Andaman with our exclusive tour packages. Book now for an unforgettable island getaway.'),
(42, 'Andaman Honeymoon Package', 'Havelock Island,Port Blair', '3N  Port Blair,  2N Havelock Island, ', 1, '10', 6, '5', 48000, 'couple', '2024-07-30', 'Andaman Honeymoon Package.jpg', 10, 'To enjoy the most romantic experiences in the Andaman Islands, come along on our 5 nights, 6 day Andaman honeymoon package. Because of their glistening blue waters, Andaman and Nicobar are also known as India\'s Own Maldives and are very popular destinations for romantic couples. The typical items, such as meals, excursions, transportation, and lodging, are included in this specially designed itinerary for the Andaman Nicobar honeymoon package. You and your special someone will get to view Radhanagar Beach, which is featured in the Times Magazine, as well as the Blue Flag beach. You will see the Sound and Light Show at Port Blair, where your Andaman Nicobar trip package begins and ends for the couple.', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '', '', 1, 'Havelock Island (8).jpg,Havelock Island (7).jpg', '', 'Andaman Tour Packages', 'Description: Explore the pristine beauty of Andaman with our exclusive tour packages. Book now for an unforgettable island getaway.'),
(43, 'Adventure into Andaman & Nicobar', 'Havelock Island,Neil Island,Port Blair', '1N Port Blair, 2N Havelock Island, 1N Neil Island', 1, '10', 4, '3', 17900, 'person', '2024-07-30', 'Neil Island (2).jpg', 10, 'White sand beaches may be found on the Andaman and Nicobar islands, where you can unwind, enjoy the sun, and partake in a variety of daring water sports. The well-thought-out itinerary of the Exotic 5 Nights 6 Days Andaman package is designed to provide you with an unforgettable vacation. Your Andaman vacation will include visits to Radhanagar Beach, Elephant Beach for snorkeling, a light and sound display within the Cellular Jail, coral reefs to see the variety of marine life, and leisure time at Bharatpur and Laxmanpur beaches. You can unwind in the Andaman and Nicobar Islands, apart from the hustle and bustle of the city.\r\n\r\nNote that this is merely a proposed itinerary to give you an idea of what might be feasible. We customise vacations to meet your needs. Please get in touch with us if you would like changes made so that we can customise a trip to meet your needs and create an incredible India tour.\r\n', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'Neil Island.jpg,Port Blair (5).jpg,Port Blair (7).jpg', '', 'Andaman Tour Packages', 'Description: Explore the pristine beauty of Andaman with our exclusive tour packages. Book now for an unforgettable island getaway.'),
(44, 'Best of Andaman Trip', 'Havelock Island,Neil Island,Port Blair', '1N Port Blair, 2N Havelock Island, 2N Neil Island', 1, '10', 6, '5', 19400, 'person', '2024-07-30', 'andamanNicobar (2).jpg', 10, 'Embark on an unforgettable journey to the mesmerizing Andaman Islands with Sky Globals. This 6-day, 5-night trip promises a perfect blend of adventure, relaxation, and natural beauty. Your journey begins in Port Blair, the capital city known for its historic charm and scenic vistas. Explore the Cellular Jail, a poignant reminder of India\'s struggle for independence, and enjoy the enchanting Light and Sound Show.\r\n\r\nNext, set sail to the tranquil Neil Island, renowned for its pristine beaches and vibrant coral reefs. Bask in the serene beauty of Laxmanpur and Bharatpur Beaches, and take in the breathtaking views from the Natural Bridge, a stunning natural rock formation.\r\n\r\nThe adventure continues as you head to Havelock Island, a paradise for beach lovers and water sports enthusiasts. Relax on the powdery sands of Radhanagar Beach, often cited as one of Asia\'s best beaches, and dive into the crystal-clear waters of Elephant Beach for an exhilarating snorkeling experience. Indulge in the vibrant underwater world, teeming with colorful marine life and coral gardens.\r\n\r\nThroughout your trip, Sky Globals ensures a seamless and comfortable experience with carefully curated itineraries, comfortable accommodations, and expert guides. Whether you\'re seeking tranquility, adventure, or a mix of both, this Andaman tour offers an unparalleled opportunity to explore some of India\'s most stunning landscapes.\r\n\r\nThis comprehensive description highlights the key attractions and experiences that travelers can expect during their Andaman trip with Sky Globals.', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'andamanNikobar.jpg,andamanNicobar (4).jpg,andamanNicobar.jpg', '', 'Andaman Tour Packages', 'Description: Explore the pristine beauty of Andaman with our exclusive tour packages. Book now for an unforgettable island getaway.'),
(45, 'Traveling to Ladakh', 'Leh,Pangong Lake, Nubra Valley', '2N Leh, 2N Nubra Valley, 2N Pangong Lake, ', 1, '11', 7, '6', 22500, 'person', '2024-07-30', 'Leh (3).jpg', 11, 'One of the most well-liked tourist destinations in India can be experienced by you with our 7-day Journey to Ladakh vacation package. Some of Ladakh\'s treasures, such Nubra Valley and Pangong Lake, are included in this well designed Leh Ladakh itinerary by SkyÂ Globals. Enjoy shopping and sightseeing in Leh, Pangong Lake bird watching, and Nubra Valley camel safari. The trip\'s major attraction is a visit to Turtuk, a town famous for its war stories from 1971. This 7-day Ladakh tour package will take you on an amazing adventure that will wow you at every turn.\r\n\r\nSky GlobalsÂ guarantees a stress-free trip with inclusions like comfortable accommodations, smooth transfers, and our knowledgeable guides who are well-versed in the history and culture of the area. So, book your tour now for an exciting Ladakh vacation! Note: This is an example itinerary; we create packages to fit your interests and financial constraints. Get in touch with our travel experts if you would like changes so we can tailor a trip to your preferences for an amazing Ladakh tour.', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'Nubra Valley (6).jpg,Nubra Valley (5).jpg', '', 'Ladakh Tour Packages', ''),
(46, 'Treasures of Ladakh', 'Delhi,Leh, Nubra Valley', '1N Delhi, 2N Leh, 2N Nubra Valley,', 1, '11', 6, '5', 17890, 'person', '2024-07-30', 'Nubra Valley (5).jpg', 11, 'You may explore the magnificent mountains with this 6-day Leh Ladakh tour package, which will make you feel grateful and appreciate the wonders of nature. One of the most significant monasteries in central Ladakh, Spituk Monastery, is visited for the entire day during this magnificent Ladakh tour. After that, travel to Nubra Valley over the Khardungla Pass, which is thought to be the highest motorable pass in the world. As you continue your journey, stop by the Samstanling Monastery in Keygar Village. You will have a full day excursion to Pangong Lake as part of our travel package. Overall, this trip allows you to experience the best of Ladakh. \r\n\r\nNote: This is only a suggested itinerary that you can change to suit your preferences and areas of interest. \r\n', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, '_Heaven Leh Ladakh.jpg,Leh.jpg', '', 'Ladakh Tour Packages', ''),
(47, 'Ladakh Tour With Kashmir', 'Leh,Pahalgam,Pangong Lake,Srinagar,Sonamarg , Gulmarg', '1N Leh, 2N Pangong Lake, 1N Pahalgam, 2N Srinagar, 2N Sonamarg, 1N Gulmarg', 1, '11', 10, '9', 29700, 'person', '2024-07-30', 'Pangong Lake (8).jpg', 11, 'Prepare to be amazed by the beauty and excitement of a single trip when you choose our Ladakh & Kashmir travel package. This is a holiday where everything is available, from discovering the culture to taking in the beauty of the hills. You will visit some of the most well-known locations in the Kashmir and Ladakh region, including Srinagar, Gulmarg, Sonmarg, Pahalgam, Kargil, and Leh, with this beautifully crafted 10-day Magnificent Kashmir & Ladakh vacation package. While you will get the opportunity to spend some amazing days in Kashmir\'s natural surroundings, Ladakh\'s breathtaking scenery will wow your senses to the fullest.\r\n\r\nNote: This is merely a recommended route. Additionally, we offer customizing options. For any changes, get in touch with us.\r\n', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'Pangong Lake (8).jpg,Pangong Lake (5).jpg', '', 'Ladakh Tour Packages', ''),
(48, '5 - Days Ladakh Trip', 'Leh,Pangong Lake, Nubra Valley', '2N Leh, 1N  Nubra Valley, 1N Pangong Lake', 1, '11', 5, '4', 14800, 'person', '2024-07-30', 'Pangong Lake (6).jpg', 11, 'With this 4-night, 5-day Ladakh vacation, you may set out on an unforgettable journey. You can see some of the most well-known sights in Ladakh, such as Pangong Lake, Leh, and Nubra Valley. You can also explore the well-known Ladakh sites like Diskit Monastery, Gurudwara Pather Sahib, Magnetic Hills, and Hall of Fame while there. You\'ll be treated to quick transportation, a guided sightseeing tour, and comfortable accommodations. You are free to alter the itinerary of this tour package to suit your needs. Get in touch with us to schedule a tour or for additional information!\r\n', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'Nubra Valley .jpg,Nubra Valley (5).jpg', '', 'Ladakh Tour Packages', ''),
(49, 'Amritsar Trip With Golden Triangle', 'Agra,Delhi,jaipur ,Amritsar', '1N Delhi, 2N Agra, 3N Jaipur, 1N Amritsar', 1, '12', 8, '7', 22600, 'person', '2024-07-30', 'amritsar.jpg', 12, 'With Amritsar, the Golden Triangle Tour will visit well-known cities. The 8-day schedule is the most amazing tour that Sky GlobalsÂ offers. In a single trip, you may take in the rich culture, fascinating history, and exquisite cuisine.\r\n\r\nAdmire the outstanding architecture that displays the combined knowledge of Mughal, Parsi, and Hindu architects during our Golden Triangle tour. Enjoy a traditional meal while taking in the vibrant culture of Rajasthan. The tour will also take you to Amritsar, a holy city where you can see the Golden Temple. \r\n\r\nNote: This schedule, which shows what may be done on this Golden Triangle tour including Amritsar, is customisable. To make any changes you would want, please get in touch with us. \r\n', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'amritsar (8).jpg,amritsar2.jpg', '', 'Punjab Tour Packages', ''),
(50, 'Chandigarh Tour With Shimla Kufri Tour ', 'chandigarh,shimla,kufri', '1N Kufri, 1N chandigarh', 1, '12', 3, '2', 10000, 'person', '2024-07-30', 'chandigarh5.jpg', 12, 'Without a doubt, one of the most breathtaking destinations in India is Shimla. Our Chandigarh to Shimla with Kufri excursion is perfect if you want to spend time in the great outdoors and enjoy the nice weather. Get away from the summer heat in May and June, or spend some quality time playing in the snow in Kufri in October when it\'s chilly outside. Our journey to Shimla from Chandigarh can meet your demands whether you are visiting with family or a significant other.\r\n\r\nWe have included first-rate amenities in our Shimla Kufri tour package, such as delicious meals, cozy lodging, easy transfers, and fantastic sightseeing excursions, to make your trip more comfortable and hassle-free. For additional information, get in touch with our travel advisor and reserve one of our finely designed Shimla holiday packages.\r\n', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'chandigarh4.jpg,chandigarh3.jpg', '', 'Punjab Tour Packages', ''),
(51, 'Lakshadweep Tour for 6 - Days', 'Agatti,Bangaram,Kochi', '3N Agatti, 2N Bangaram, ', 1, '13', 6, '5', 50000, 'person', '2024-07-30', 'Lakshadweep (3).jpg', 13, 'Lakshadweep, one of the best tropical islands in South India, is the place to go for a laid-back vacation, honeymoon, scuba diving, and napping. Get the most out of this tropical paradise with our five-night, six-day Lakshadweep vacation. In addition to the Cochin city trip, you will have wonderful beach activities at Agatti and Bangaram Islands. You can indulge in sailing, scuba diving, and kayaking if you enjoy water sports.\r\n', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'agatti (12).jpg,agatti (5).jpg', '', 'Lakshadweep Tour Packages', ''),
(52, 'Lakshadweep Tour With 11+Activities', 'Agatti', '4N Agatti, ', 1, '13', 4, '3', 45800, 'person', '2024-07-30', 'agatti (5).jpg', 13, '**Explore Agatti, Lakshadweep: 3 Nights with Sky Globals**\r\n\r\nEmbark on an exhilarating 3-night adventure to Agatti in Lakshadweep with Sky Globals, where over 11 thrilling activities await. Discover the turquoise waters and white sandy beaches of this tropical paradise, perfect for snorkeling, scuba diving, and kayaking. Experience the vibrant marine life with glass-bottom boat rides and underwater excursions. Relax on pristine beaches, savor local cuisine, and soak in the tranquil island vibes. With Sky Globals\' seamless arrangements and expert guidance, your Agatti tour promises an unforgettable blend of adventure and relaxation.', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'agatti (9).jpg,agatti (10).jpg', '', 'Lakshadweep Tour Packages', ''),
(53, 'Explore Agatti ', 'Agatti', '3N Agatti, ', 1, '13', 4, '3', 25000, 'person', '2024-07-30', 'agatti (10).jpg', 13, 'Embark on a serene escape to Agatti Island with Sky Globals on a 3-night adventure. Nestled in the Lakshadweep archipelago, Agatti is a paradise of turquoise waters and pristine beaches. Delight in the tranquil beauty of coral reefs and vibrant marine life as you snorkel or dive in the clear waters. Relax on the soft sandy shores, basking in the island\'s unspoiled charm. With Sky Globals, enjoy seamless travel arrangements, cozy accommodations, and expert guidance, ensuring a perfect blend of relaxation and exploration. Discover Agatti\'s enchanting allure and create unforgettable memories in this tropical haven.', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'agatti (11).jpg,agatti (9).jpg', '', 'Lakshadweep Tour Packages', ''),
(54, 'Tour to Gangtok, Darjeeling, and Sikkim', 'Darjeeling,Gangtok', '2N Darjeeling, 2N Gangtok ', 1, '21', 5, '4', 13000, 'person', '2024-07-30', 'Gangotri (5).jpg', 21, 'With our 5 Days Sikkim Darjeeling Gangtok tour package, explore the majesty of North East India. Travel to the beautiful destinations of Darjeeling and Gangtok and experience the tranquility, witness breathtaking landscapes and breathe in the fresh air. Whether you plan a trip with your family or beloved, our Darjeeling Gangtok tour package will satiate all your travel desires and make your journey smooth and memorable.\r\n\r\nOur Darjeeling Gangtok tour packages covers all the major tourist attractions of both places. Visit Batasia Loop, Ghoom Monastery, Tea Estate, Tiger Hill, Tsomgo Lake, Rumtek Monastery, Nathula Pass, and MG Road. Book 5 days Sikkim Darjeeling Gangtok tour package from Delhi, Mumbai, Bangalore, Kolkata, Chennai, and other cities of India. Our travel experts have tastefully crafted the Darjeeling Gangtok package for a memorable trip and equipped it with excellent services like assisted tours, comfy stays, and delicious meals.', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'gangtok.jpg,gangtok4.jpg', '', 'Sikkim Tour Packages', ''),
(55, 'North East Tour\'s Treasures', 'Darjeeling,Gangtok, Kalimpong, Pelling', '2N Darjeeling, 2N Kalimpong, 3N Gangtok, 2N Pelling', 1, '21', 10, '9', 35000, 'person', '2024-07-30', 'North East Tours Treasures.jpg', 21, 'Unveil the treasures of Northeast India with Sky Globals on a 10-day, 9-night journey through Darjeeling, Pelling, Kalimpong, and Gangtok. Begin in Darjeeling, where the iconic toy train and breathtaking views of the Himalayas await. Continue to Pelling, home to the majestic Pemayangtse Monastery and stunning waterfalls. In Kalimpong, explore colonial architecture and serene landscapes. Finally, immerse yourself in the vibrant culture and natural beauty of Gangtok, visiting monasteries and enjoying panoramic vistas. With Sky Globals, experience seamless travel, comfortable stays, and expert guidance, making this an unforgettable adventure.', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'North East Tours Treasures1.jpg', '', 'Sikkim Tour Packages', ''),
(56, 'Pleasant Tour to Sikkim', 'Gangtok,Pelling', '2N Gangtok, 2N Pelling, ', 1, '21', 5, '4', 15000, 'person', '2024-07-30', 'Pleasant Tour to Sikkim.jpg', 21, 'Embark on a delightful 5-day, 4-night tour to Sikkim with Sky Globals, exploring the enchanting destinations of Pelling and Gangtok. Begin your journey in Pelling, where you\'ll be captivated by the breathtaking views of the Kanchenjunga range and the serene beauty of the monasteries. Continue to Gangtok, the vibrant capital, known for its picturesque landscapes, bustling markets, and rich cultural heritage. Enjoy seamless travel arrangements, comfortable accommodations, and expert guidance from Sky Globals, ensuring a memorable and pleasant experience as you uncover the charm and tranquility of Sikkim.', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'Pleasant Tour to Sikkim.jpg', '', 'Sikkim Tour Packages', ''),
(57, 'Sikkim Honeymoon Package', '', '', 1, '21', 7, '6', 38000, 'couple', '2024-07-30', 'Sikkim Honeymoon Package.jfif', 21, 'Experience the romance of Sikkim with Sky Globals\' 7-day, 6-night honeymoon package. Begin your journey in the charming capital, Gangtok, exploring its vibrant culture and stunning landscapes. Visit the serene Tsomgo Lake and the sacred Baba Mandir. Continue to the picturesque town of Pelling, where the majestic Kanchenjunga peaks offer a breathtaking backdrop. Explore the tranquil monasteries, cascading waterfalls, and lush greenery. With comfortable accommodations, seamless travel, and personalized services, Sky Globals ensures a memorable and enchanting honeymoon in the serene beauty of Sikkim.', '0', '0', '0', '0', 0, '', '', 1, 'Sikkim Honeymoon Package.jfif', '', 'Sikkim Tour Packages', ''),
(58, 'Kerala Tamilnadu Tour', 'Coimbatore,Kochi,Kumarakom,Munnar,Ooty,Thekkady ', '', 1, '23', 9, '8', 24000, 'person', '2024-07-30', 'tamilnadu (5).jpg', 23, 'Experience the best of South India with Sky Globals on a captivating 9-day Kerala and Tamil Nadu tour. Begin your journey in the lush landscapes of Kerala, exploring the serene backwaters of Alleppey, the wildlife at Periyar, and the hill station charm of Munnar. Transition to Tamil Nadu, where the cultural richness of Madurai\'s Meenakshi Temple, the French colonial vibes of Pondicherry, and the historical grandeur of Mahabalipuram await. With Sky Globals, enjoy expertly planned itineraries, comfortable accommodations, and immersive experiences that showcase the vibrant heritage and natural beauty of these enchanting states.', '0', '0', '0', '0', 0, '', '', 1, 'tamilnadu (2).jpg', '', 'Tamil Nadu Tour Packages', ''),
(59, 'Rameshwaram Kanyakumari Temple Tour with Madurai', 'Kanyakumari ,Madurai ,Rameswaram ', '', 1, '23', 4, '3', 10000, 'person', '2024-07-30', 'tamilnadu (6).jpg', 23, 'One of South India\'s greatest assets has always been its spirituality, which you may experience throughout the three nights and four days of the Madurai Rameshwaram Kanyakumari Tour Package. When followers are unable to control their thoughts, they gravitate toward the homes of the gods in search of the greatest comfort. You could become weary of counting the temples scattered over this area, but the list will never end.\r\n\r\nWe have combined the top three sites in Tamil Nadu into our Tamil Nadu Pilgrimage Tour because the state is regarded as having a higher level of spiritual enlightenment than other states in South India. This well designed schedule visits Madurai, the home of the Goddess', '0', '0', '0', '0', 0, '', '', 1, 'tamilnadu (5).jpg', '', 'Tamil Nadu Tour Packages', ''),
(60, 'South India Golden Triangle Tour', 'Bangalore,Coonoor,Mysore,Ooty', '', 1, '23', 8, '7', 22000, 'person', '2024-07-30', 'South India Golden Triangle Tour.avif', 23, 'Karnataka has always been a popular tourism destination because of its rich past, abundance of pilgrimage sites, and stunning natural surroundings. One will never grow tired of this region for a number of reasons, from its amazing historical attractions to its flamboyant architecture, wealth of natural beauty, and abundance of daring spots. The Karnataka Golden Triangle Tour is one of the best trips that covers a significant portion of what this state has to offer tourists.\r\n\r\nRemembering that eight-day Karnataka travel packages cover the majority of the main destinations, they are comprehensive packages. Additionally, we have created numerous packages with the needs of each and every tourist in mind. The package for the weeklong South IndiaÂ Golden Triangle Tour is among our best recommendations for you.', '0', '0', '0', '0', 0, '', '', 1, 'South India Golden Triangle Tour.avif', '', 'Tamil Nadu Tour Packages', ''),
(61, 'Beautiful South India Holiday', 'Mysore,Ooty', '', 1, '23', 5, '4', 23000, 'person', '2024-07-30', 'Bengaluru.webp', 23, 'Experience the charm of South India with Sky Globals on a 5-day holiday covering Mysore and Ooty. Start your journey in Mysore, where the grandeur of Mysore Palace and the vibrant local markets will captivate you. Continue to the lush hills of Ooty, known as the \"Queen of Hill Stations,\" where you\'ll be enchanted by its picturesque landscapes, sprawling tea gardens, and serene lakes. With Sky Globals, enjoy comfortable accommodations, well-planned itineraries, and expert guides, ensuring a memorable and hassle-free getaway. Discover the cultural richness and natural beauty of South India on this delightful holiday.', '0', '0', '0', '0', 0, '', '', 1, 'Bengaluru.webp', '', 'Tamil Nadu Tour Packages', ''),
(62, 'Vietnam Tour Package For 5 - Days', '', '', 2, '35,105', 5, '4', 30000, 'person', '2024-07-31', '5 Days Vietnam Tour.jpg', 0, 'Our carefully planned five-day Vietnam travel package includes breathtaking scenery of the bays and historic caves. Vietnam\'s natural attractiveness adds to the enjoyment of this journey. Vietnam ought to be your first choice for travel. Vietnam boasts the best natural resources, ranging from rich, which provides for breathtaking photographs. You can get to see all of it on our 5-day journey in Vietnam. The package includes a boat ride through Vietnam\'s rural countryside, mountains, fields, and caverns; it also includes touring Northern Vietnam\'s old temples and much more. This Vietnam package also includes sightseeing tours, transfers, meals, and lodging to provide a relaxed vacation. You can view the five-day tour\'s schedule for Vietnam below for additional information.\r\n\r\nNote: This is merely an example of a proposed 5-day Vietnam vacation package; it shows you what might be possible. Through communication with our travel experts, you may personalize this Vietnam vacation from India.\r\n', '0', '0', '0', '0', 0, '', '', 1, '5 Days Vietnam Tour.jpg', '', 'Vietnam Tour Packages', ''),
