(81, 'Charming Maldives Tour', '', '', 6, '', 5, '4', 40000, 'person', '2024-08-01', 'Charming Maldives Tour.jpg', 0, 'Experience the charm of the Maldives with a 5-day tour by Sky Globals. Immerse yourself in the crystal-clear turquoise waters, pristine white sandy beaches, and vibrant marine life. Indulge in luxurious beachfront accommodations and savor exquisite local and international cuisine. Enjoy activities such as snorkeling, diving, and island hopping, or simply relax and unwind in this tropical paradise. Whether you\'re seeking adventure or tranquility, this budget-friendly tour offers the perfect escape to the mesmerizing beauty of the Maldives.', '0', '0', '0', '0', 0, '', '', 1, 'Charming Maldives Tour.jpg', '', 'Maldives Tour Packages', ''),
