(156, 'The Ultimate Package for Bangkok & Pattaya', '', '2N Pattaya, 1N Coral Island, 2N Bangkok ', 28, '40,41', 6, '5', 45000, 'person', '2024-08-07', 'The Ultimate Package for Bangkok & Pattaya.jpg', 0, 'Experience the best of Thailand with Skyglobals\' 6-day Ultimate Package for Bangkok & Pattaya. Dive into the vibrant city life of Bangkok, exploring iconic landmarks like the Grand Palace and Wat Arun, and indulge in the bustling markets and delicious street food. Then, relax on the pristine beaches of Pattaya, enjoy water sports, and visit the famous Coral Island. This package combines cultural exploration and beachside relaxation for an unforgettable Thai adventure.', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'The Ultimate Package for Bangkok & Pattaya.jpg,The Ultimate Package for Bangkok & Pattaya9.jpg,The Ultimate Package for Bangkok & Pattaya8.jpg,The Ultimate Package for Bangkok & Pattaya7.jpg,The Ultimate Package for Bangkok & Pattaya6.jpg,The Ultimate Package for Bangkok & Pattaya5.jpg,The Ultimate Package for Bangkok & Pattaya4.jpg,The Ultimate Package for Bangkok & Pattaya3.jpg,The Ultimate Package for Bangkok & Pattaya2.jpg,The Ultimate Package for Bangkok & Pattaya1.jpg', '', 'Thailand Tour Packages', 'Description: Discover the beauty of Thailand with our exclusive tour packages. Explore stunning beaches, vibrant cities, and rich cultural heritage. Book now!'),
(157, 'Thailand Romantic Place', '', '2N Krabi, 1N Railay Beach, 2N Phuket, 1N Phi Phi Islands, 2 Pattaya ', 28, '38,39,40,41', 9, '8', 52800, 'person', '2024-08-07', 'Thailand Romantic Place.jpg', 0, 'Skyglobals offers an enchanting 9-day romantic getaway in Thailand, where couples can immerse themselves in the allure of pristine beaches, vibrant culture, and serene landscapes. Begin your journey in the bustling city of Bangkok, exploring its majestic temples and bustling markets. Then, escape to the tranquil paradise of Phuket, known for its stunning sunsets, crystal-clear waters, and luxurious resorts. Conclude your trip with a visit to the picturesque Phi Phi Islands, where you can indulge in romantic boat rides and secluded beach picnics. This carefully curated itinerary ensures an unforgettable romantic experience, blending adventure, relaxation, and intimacy.', 'Flights', 'Meals', 'Transfers', '0', 0, '4', '', 1, 'Thailand Romantic Place.jpg,Thailand Romantic Place9.png,Thailand Romantic Place8.jpg,Thailand Romantic Place7.jpg,Thailand Romantic Place6.jpg,Thailand Romantic Place5.jpg,Thailand Romantic Place4.jpg,Thailand Romantic Place3.jpg,Thailand Romantic Place2.jpg,Thailand Romantic Place1.jpg', '', 'Thailand Tour Packages', 'Description: Discover the beauty of Thailand with our exclusive tour packages. Explore stunning beaches, vibrant cities, and rich cultural heritage. Book now!'),
(158, 'Thrilling Thailand', '', '', 16, '39,40,107,108', 5, '4', 51999, 'person', '2024-08-07', 'Thrilling Thailand.webp', 0, 'The \"Thrilling Thailand\" package with Skyglobals offers an exhilarating 5-day adventure through some of Thailand\'s most iconic destinations. Experience the vibrant streets of Bangkok, with its bustling markets, majestic temples, and lively nightlife. Then, relax on the pristine beaches of Pattaya, enjoying water sports, beachside activities, and stunning sunsets. This package ensures a perfect blend of excitement and relaxation, making it an unforgettable getaway in the Land of Smiles.', '0', '0', '0', '0', 0, '', '', 1, 'Thrilling Thailand.webp', '', '', 'Description: Discover the beauty of Thailand with our exclusive tour packages. Explore stunning beaches, vibrant cities, and rich cultural heritage. Book now!'),
(159, '7-Day Greece', '', '', 11, '76,109,110', 7, '6', 126252, 'person', '2024-08-07', '7-DayGreece700x400.jpg', 0, 'Skyglobals offers an enchanting 7-day Greece package, providing a perfect blend of history, culture, and stunning landscapes. This tour includes visits to iconic destinations such as Athens, Santorini, and Mykonos, allowing travelers to explore ancient ruins, vibrant markets, and beautiful beaches. With carefully curated itineraries and exceptional accommodations, this package ensures a memorable Greek adventure.', '0', '0', '0', '0', 0, '', '', 1, '7-DayGreece700x400.jpg', '', 'Greece Tour Packages', ''),
(160, 'Mauritius Magic', '', '', 10, '155,156', 6, '5', 87999, 'person', '2024-08-07', 'Mauritius Magic.jpg', 0, 'Experience the enchanting beauty of Mauritius with the \"Mauritius Magic\" package from Skyglobals. Over six days, immerse yourself in the island\'s pristine beaches, vibrant culture, and lush landscapes. From exploring the stunning coral reefs to enjoying the luxurious resorts, this package offers a perfect blend of relaxation and adventure. Discover the island\'s hidden gems and create unforgettable memories in one of the most idyllic destinations in the Indian Ocean.', '0', '0', '0', '0', 0, '', '', 1, 'Mauritius Magic.jpg', '', 'Mauritius Tour Packages', ''),
(161, '  Joyful Malaysia journey', '', '', 31, '168', 5, '4', 18900, 'person', '2024-08-22', 'Joyful Malaysia.jpg', 0, 'Embark on a delightful 5-day, 4-night \'Joyful Malaysia Kuala Lumpur Tour\' with Skyglobals. Dive into the vibrant energy of Malaysia\'s capital city, where culture meets modernity. Discover iconic landmarks like the Petronas Twin Towers, explore bustling markets, and savor delicious local cuisine. Take a stroll through beautiful parks, and visit impressive religious sites like Batu Caves. The tour offers a perfect blend of sightseeing, shopping, and relaxation, ensuring an unforgettable experience in Kuala Lumpur. Whether you\'re a history buff or a nature lover, this tour is crafted to showcase the best of Malaysia.', '0', '0', '0', '0', 0, '', '', 1, 'Joyful Malaysia.jpg', '', '', ''),
(162, 'Malaysia Tour For 5 - Days', '', '', 31, '168,169,170', 5, '4', 18900, 'Adult', '2024-08-22', 'Malaysia Tour For 5 - Days.jpg', 0, 'Embark on an unforgettable 5-day, 4-night Malaysia tour with Skyglobals, where youâ€™ll explore the best of Kuala Lumpur, Genting, and Langkawi. Begin your journey in Kuala Lumpur, the vibrant capital city, with its iconic Petronas Twin Towers, bustling markets, and cultural landmarks. Then, venture to Genting, a highland retreat known for its cool climate, casinos, and thrilling theme parks. Finally, unwind on the stunning beaches of Langkawi, where turquoise waters and breathtaking landscapes provide the perfect escape. This tour blends adventure, relaxation, and cultural exploration, making it ideal for every traveler.', '0', '0', '0', '0', 0, '', '', 1, 'Malaysia Tour For 5 - Days.jpg', '', '', ''),
(163, 'Malaysia Tour with Singapore', '', '', 31, '', 6, '5', 50000, 'Adult', '2024-08-22', 'Malaysia tour With Singapore.jpg', 0, 'For your 6-day, 5-night Malaysia and Singapore tour with Skyglobals, here\'s a brief paragraph for tourists:\r\n\r\n\"Discover the perfect blend of vibrant city life and tranquil beauty on this exciting 6-day, 5-night tour of Malaysia and Singapore. Begin your journey in the dynamic city of Kuala Lumpur, where stunning skyscrapers meet cultural gems. Explore the iconic Petronas Towers, colorful Batu Caves, and indulge in local delicacies. Then, head to the picturesque island of Langkawi, known for its breathtaking beaches and lush greenery. Finally, experience the bustling city-state of Singapore, where youâ€™ll marvel at the futuristic Gardens by the Bay, stroll along Marina Bay Sands, and enjoy the diverse, multicultural atmosphere. This tour promises unforgettable memories of both Malaysia and Singapore\'s finest highlights.\"', '0', '0', '0', '0', 0, '', '', 1, 'Malaysia tour With Singapore.jpg', '', '', '');
