(16, 1, 42, '1', 'Delhi to Shimla', 'Depart from Delhi to Shimla early in the morning (approximately 8-9 hours drive). Arrive in Shimla and check into your hotel. Spend the evening exploring the Mall Road and Ridge Road, enjoying the colonial architecture, shops, and cafes. Overnight stay in', 'Red Fort, Akshardham, Qutb Minar,  India Gate, Raj Ghat', '1', 'harshit', '2024-06-10'),
(17, 1, 1, '2', 'Shimla Sightseeing', ' Visit the Viceregal Lodge (Rashtrapati Niwas), former summer residence of British viceroys, and its surrounding gardens. Explore the Himachal State Museum to learn about the history and culture of the region. Take a scenic drive to Kufri, a small hill station.', 'Mall Road, Shri Hanuman Mandir Jakhoo, Green Valley', '1', 'harshit', '2024-06-10'),
(18, 1, 2, '3', 'Shimla to Manali', 'Depart from Shimla to Manali early in the morning (approximately 7-8 hours drive). En route, stop at Pandoh Dam for photography and enjoying the scenic views. Arrive in Manali and check into your hotel. Spend the evening exploring the local markets and so', 'Hadimba Temple, Manu Temple, Naggar Castle, Rohtang Pass, Hamta Pass ', '1', 'harshit', '2024-06-10'),
(19, 1, 0, '4', 'Rohtang Pass Excursion', 'Depart early morning for an excursion to Rohtang Pass (subject to availability and weather conditions). Enjoy the scenic drive through picturesque landscapes and stop at Marhi for refreshments. Spend the day at Rohtang Pass, indulging in snow activities (', '', '1', 'harshit', '2024-06-10'),
(20, 1, 0, '5', ' Solang Valley Adventure', 'Head to Solang Valley for a day of adventure activities such as paragliding, zorbing, and rope-way rides. Enjoy lunch at one of the cafes overlooking the valley. Optionally, visit the Anjani Mahadev Temple and trek to the beautiful waterfall nearby. Retur', '', '1', 'harshit', '2024-06-10'),
(24, 1, 0, '6', 'Manali Local Sightseeing', 'Explore more of Manali local attractions, including Hadimba Devi Temple, Tibetan Monastery, and Van Vihar National Park. Visit the Vashisht Temple and hot water springs for a relaxing dip. Enjoy shopping for souvenirs and local handicrafts in the markets.', '', '1', 'harshit', '2024-06-10'),
(25, 1, 0, '7', 'Return to Delhi', 'After breakfast, check out from the hotel and depart for Delhi. Arrive in Delhi by evening, concluding your memorable trip to Shimla, Kufri, Manali, and Rohtang Pass.', '', '1', 'harshit', '2024-06-10'),
(26, 2, 42, '1', 'Delhi', 'Explore historical landmarks like the Red Fort, Qutub Minar, and Humayun Tomb. Visit the vibrant markets of Chandni Chowk and Connaught Place. Experience the spiritual ambiance of Lotus Temple and Akshardham Temple. Enjoy a taste of Delhi street food.', 'Red Fort, Akshardham, Qutb Minar,  India Gate, Raj Ghat', '1', 'harshit', '2024-06-11'),
(28, 2, 1, '2', 'Shimla', 'Drive or take a train to Shimla, enjoying the scenic views along the way. Explore the Mall Road, Ridge, and Christ Church. Visit the Viceregal Lodge and Himachal State Museum. Take a leisurely stroll in the lush greenery of Shimla parks.', 'Mall Road, Shri Hanuman Mandir Jakhoo, Green Valley', '1', 'harshit', '2024-06-11'),
(30, 2, 0, '3', 'Kufri', 'Spend a day in Kufri, known for its picturesque landscapes and adventure activities. Enjoy horse riding, skiing (in season), and trekking. Visit the Himalayan Nature Park to see local flora and fauna.', '', '1', 'harshit', '2024-06-11'),
(31, 2, 2, '4', 'Manali', 'Drive through scenic routes to Manali. Explore the charming old Manali and its vibrant markets. Visit Hadimba Temple, Tibetan Monasteries, and Van Vihar. Experience adventure sports like paragliding and river rafting (seasonal).', 'Hadimba Temple, Manu Temple, Naggar Castle, Rohtang Pass, Hamta Pass ', '1', 'harshit', '2024-06-11'),
(33, 2, 0, '5', 'Rohtang Pass', 'Embark on an exhilarating day trip to Rohtang Pass (subject to weather and permit availability). Enjoy breathtaking views of snow-capped peaks and glaciers. Engage in activities like snowboarding and sledging.', '', '1', 'harshit', '2024-06-11'),
(34, 2, 77, '6', 'Arrival at Dharamshala', 'Drive to Dharamshala, the abode of the Dalai Lama. Explore McLeod Ganj, the Tibetan cultural hub. Visit the Namgyal Monastery and the Tibetan Museum. Trek to Triund for panoramic views of the Dhauladhar range.', 'Residence of Dalai Lama, Tiesto Monasterio, Kangda Fort, Mcleodganj ', '1', 'harshit', '2024-06-11'),
(36, 2, 0, '7', 'Dharamshala', 'Drive to Dharamshala, the abode of the Dalai Lama. Explore McLeod Ganj, the Tibetan cultural hub. Visit the Namgyal Monastery and the Tibetan Museum. Trek to Triund for panoramic views of the Dhauladhar range.', '', '1', 'harshit', '2024-06-11'),
(37, 2, 35, '8', 'Arrival at Dalhousie', 'Drive to Dalhousie, known for its colonial charm and scenic beauty. Explore the quaint streets and colonial architecture. Visit St. Johns Church, Panchpula, and Satdhara Falls. Take a day trip to Khajjiar, often referred to as the (Mini Switzerland of India).', 'Beeji\'s Park, Dainkund Peak, Garam Sadak, Kalatop Khajjiar Sanctuary, Panchpula', '1', 'harshit', '2024-06-11'),
