(101, 3, 34, '1', 'Arrival in Chandigarh', 'Arrive in Chandigarh.Explore this unique garden made from industrial & home waste.Enjoy boating and a peaceful walk around the lake.Shop and dine at one of Chandigarh\'s most vibrant areas.', 'Rock Garden,Sukhna Lake,Sector 17 Plaza', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-07-30'),
(102, 3, 1, '2', 'Chandigarh to Shimla', 'Depart for Shimla (approx. 3.5 hours drive).Check-in at hotel and relax.Walk around, shop, and enjoy local delicacies.Visit the second oldest church in North India, known for its stained glass windows.', 'The Ridge and Mall Road,Christ Church', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-07-30'),
(103, 3, 1, '3', 'Shimla', 'Visit this temple dedicated to Lord Hanuman, offering panoramic views.A small hill station famous for its scenic beauty and adventure activities.Tour this historic building, the former residence of the British Viceroy of India.Learn about Himachali culture, heritage, and art.Leisure time at the hotel or explore local markets.', 'Jakhoo Temple,Kufri,Viceregal Lodge,State Museum', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-07-30'),
(104, 3, 289, '4', 'Shimla to Chail to Nalagarh', 'Depart for Chail (approx. 2 hours drive).Tour this beautiful palace built by the Maharaja of Patiala.Visit the world\'s highest cricket ground.Head to Nalagarh (approx. 3 hours drive), check-in at hotel.', 'Chail Palace,Cricket Ground', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-07-30'),
(105, 3, 131, '5', 'Nalagarh to Dharamshala', 'Depart for Dharamshala (approx. 5.5 hours drive).Check-in at hotel and relax.Visit the Tibetan Market and explore local Tibetan culture.Explore local markets or enjoy a peaceful evening at the hotel.', 'McLeod Ganj', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-07-30'),
(106, 3, 129, '6', 'Dharamshala', 'Visit this spiritual center and residence of the Dalai Lama.Enjoy a small trek to this beautiful waterfall.Explore this small mid-altitude lake surrounded by deodar trees.Enjoy panoramic views of the Dhauladhar range.Relax at the hotel or visit local cafes.', 'Dalai Lama Temple Complex,Bhagsu Waterfall,Dal Lake,Naddi View Point', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-07-30'),
