(358, 35, 39, '4', ' Agra to Jaipur via Fatehpur Sikri (240 km, 5-6 hours)', 'Depart from Agra to Jaipur, stopping en route at Fatehpur Sikri, a historical city.  Arrive in Jaipur and check into your hotel. Visit the City Palace and Jantar Mantar, an astronomical observatory. Explore the local markets around Hawa Mahal (Palace of Winds).', 'Fatehpur Sikri,City Palace, Jantar Mantar,Hawa Mahal', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-01'),
