(360, 35, 41, '6', 'Jaipur to Mandawa (170 km, 3-4 hours)', 'Depart from Jaipur to Mandawa. Arrive in Mandawa and check into your hotel. Explore the Mandawa Fort and its intricate architecture. Visit the famous havelis (mansions) of Mandawa, known for their beautiful frescoes. Stroll through the quaint lanes of Mandawa, admiring the rich cultural heritage.', 'Mandawa Fort,havelis', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-01'),
