(379, 40, 56, '3', 'Varanasi', 'Take an early morning boat ride on the Ganges River to witness the sunrise and the rituals performed on the ghats. Visit Sarnath, where Lord Buddha gave his first sermon after attaining enlightenment. Explore the Banaras Hindu University (BHU) and visit the Bharat Kala Bhavan Museum. Visit the Durga Temple and Tulsi Manas Temple. Stroll through the narrow lanes of Varanasi and explore the local markets for souvenirs.', 'Ganges River,Sarnath,Banaras Hindu University,Bharat Kala Bhavan Museum,Durga Temple ,Tulsi Manas Temple', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-01'),
