(387, 41, 60, '7', 'Port Blair and Departure', 'Visit the Ross Island, which was the administrative headquarters of the British in the Andaman Islands. Visit the Corbyn\'s Cove Beach for a last dip in the sea before your departure. Depending on your flight schedule, do some last-minute shopping for souvenirs. Head to the airport for your onward journey.', 'Ross Island,Corbyns Cove Beach', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-01'),
(388, 42, 60, '1', 'Arrival in Port Blair', 'Arrive at Port Blair. Check into your honeymoon suite and freshen up. Visit the Cellular Jail and explore its historical significance. Enjoy a leisurely walk through Corbyn\'s Cove Beach for a relaxed beach experience. Attend the Light and Sound Show at Cellular Jail, which narrates the saga of India\'s freedom struggle.', 'Cellular Jail,Corbyns Cove Beach, Light and Sound Show', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-01'),
