(404, 45, 112, '1', 'Arrival in Leh', 'Arrive in Leh. Check into your hotel and rest to acclimatize to the altitude.  Take a leisurely walk around Leh to explore local markets and sights. Visit the Shanti Stupa for panoramic views of Leh and the surrounding mountains. Explore the Leh Palace and get a glimpse of Ladakh\'s history and culture.', 'Shanti Stupa,Leh Palace', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-01'),
(405, 45, 112, '2', 'Leh Local Sightseeing', 'Visit Hemis Monastery, one of the largest and wealthiest monasteries in Ladakh. Explore Thiksey Monastery, known for its impressive architecture and beautiful statues. Visit the Shey Palace and its monastery, which offers fantastic views of the valley. Explore Stok Palace and the nearby Stok Monastery, home to the royal family of Ladakh. Enjoy dinner at a local restaurant in Leh.', 'Hemis Monastery,Thiksey Monastery,Shey Palace,Stok Palace,Stok Monastery', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-01'),
(406, 45, 112, '3', 'Leh to Nubra Valley', 'Depart from Leh to Nubra Valley via the Khardung La Pass (5,359 meters), one of the highest motorable roads in the world.  Arrive in Nubra Valley and check into your camp or hotel. Visit Diskit Monastery, which offers beautiful views of the valley. Explore the Hemis Shukpachan Village to experience traditional Ladakhi culture. Relax and enjoy the serene atmosphere of Nubra Valley.', 'Khardung La Pass, Diskit Monastery,Hemis Shukpachan Village', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-01'),
(407, 45, 66, '4', 'Nubra Valley Exploration', 'Visit the Sand Dunes at Hunder and enjoy a ride on a Bactrian camel (double-humped camel). Explore Sumur Village and its picturesque landscapes. Visit the Panamik Hot Springs for a relaxing soak in natural hot springs. Return to your camp or hotel and enjoy a peaceful evening.', 'Sand Dunes at Hunder,Sumur Village,Panamik Hot Springs', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-01'),
(408, 45, 65, '5', 'Nubra Valley to Pangong Lake', 'Depart from Nubra Valley to Pangong Lake via the Shyok River Road (a less frequented route) or return via Leh and cross the Chang La Pass. Arrive at Pangong Lake and check into your camp or guesthouse. Enjoy the breathtaking views of the lake, known for its ever-changing hues. Relax by the lake and enjoy the serene environment.', 'Shyok River Road,Chang La Pass', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-01'),
(409, 45, 0, '6', 'Pangong Lake to Leh', 'Enjoy a sunrise view over Pangong Lake and explore the surrounding areas.  Depart from Pangong Lake and head back to Leh. Arrive in Leh and enjoy some leisure time or explore local markets for souvenirs.', '', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-01'),
(410, 45, 0, '7', 'Departure from Leh', 'Depending on your flight schedule, you can visit any remaining local sights or relax at the hotel. Check out of your hotel and head to the airport for your onward journey.', '', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-01'),
(411, 46, 42, '1', 'Arrival in Delhi', 'Arrive in Delhi. Check into your hotel and freshen up. Visit India Gate, Rashtrapati Bhavan, and Parliament House for iconic views of the capital. Explore Qutub Minar and Humayun\'s Tomb to experience Delhiâ€™s historical architecture. Stroll through Connaught Place or India Habitat Centre for shopping and dining.', ' India Gate,Rashtrapati Bhavan,Parliament House,Qutub Minar,Humayun,Connaught Places Tomb', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-01'),
