(508, 65, 35, '1', 'Arrival in Hanoi', 'Arrive in Hanoi and transfer to your hotel for check-in. In the afternoon, visit Hoan Kiem Lake and Ngoc Son Temple, and explore the bustling Old Quarter with its lively markets and historic architecture. In the evening, enjoy a traditional Vietnamese dinner and attend a Water Puppet Show at the Thang Long Water Puppet Theatre.', 'Hoan Kiem Lake,Ngoc Son Temple,Old Quarter,Water Puppet Show', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-22'),
(509, 65, 35, '2', 'Explore Hanoi', 'Begin your day with a visit to the Ho Chi Minh Mausoleum and Presidential Palace, followed by a tour of the Temple of Literature, Vietnamâ€™s first university. In the afternoon, explore the Vietnam Museum of Ethnology and stroll through the French Quarter to see the Opera House and colonial-era buildings. Enjoy dinner at a local restaurant and visit the Night Market in the Old Quarter in the evening.', 'Ho Chi Minh Mausoleum,Presidential Palace,Temple of Literature,Vietnam Museum of Ethnology,French Quarter,Opera House,Night Market', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-22'),
(510, 65, 36, '3', 'Travel to Da Nang', 'Fly to Da Nang in the morning and check into your hotel. Spend the afternoon relaxing on My Khe Beach and exploring the Marble Mountains, known for their caves and pagodas. In the evening, take a stroll along the Han River and admire the Dragon Bridge, which features a nightly fire-breathing show.', 'My Khe Beach,Marble Mountains,Han River,Dragon Bridge', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-22'),
(511, 65, 295, '4', 'Hoi An Day Trip', 'Drive to Hoi An in the morning and explore the Ancient Town, including the Japanese Covered Bridge, Tan Ky Old House, and the bustling Hoi An Market. In the afternoon, either participate in a cooking class to learn about local cuisine or visit a tailor shop for custom clothing, then relax at An Bang Beach. Return to Da Nang in the evening for dinner.', 'Hoi An,Ancient Town,Japanese Covered Bridge,,Tan Ky Old House,Hoi An Market,An Bang Beach', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-22'),
(512, 65, 37, '5', 'Travel to Ho Chi Minh City', 'Fly to Ho Chi Minh City in the morning and check into your hotel. Spend the afternoon visiting the War Remnants Museum, followed by a tour of the Notre-Dame Cathedral Basilica of Saigon and the Central Post Office, both showcasing French colonial architecture. In the evening, enjoy dinner on Bui Vien Street and explore the city\'s vibrant nightlife.', 'War Remnants Museum,Notre-Dame Cathedral Basilica of Saigon,Central Post Office,Bui Vien Street', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-22'),
(513, 65, 37, '6', 'Explore Ho Chi Minh City', 'In the morning, take a trip to the Cu Chi Tunnels to learn about their historical significance during the Vietnam War. Return to Ho Chi Minh City in the afternoon to visit Ben Thanh Market for souvenirs and local products, and explore the Jade Emperor Pagoda. In the evening, enjoy a dinner cruise on the Saigon River with scenic views of the city.', 'Cu Chi Tunnels,Ben Thanh Market,Jade Emperor Pagoda,dinner cruise', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-22'),
(514, 65, 0, '7', 'Departure', 'Enjoy a leisurely morning with free time for last-minute shopping or exploring local attractions. In the afternoon, transfer to the airport for your departure flight.', '', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-22'),
(515, 66, 3, '1', 'Arrival and City Highlights', 'Arrive in Singapore and embark on a Singapore City Tour to explore highlights such as Marina Bay Sands, Gardens by the Bay, and the iconic Merlion Park. In the afternoon, visit Chinatown for local shopping and food. In the evening, enjoy a Singapore River Cruise to see the city\'s skyline from the water.', 'Singapore City Tour,Marina Bay Sands, Gardens by the Bay,Merlion Park,Chinatown,Singapore River Cruise', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-22');
