(516, 66, 207, '2', 'Sentosa Island Adventure', 'Start your day with a visit to Sentosa Island, where you can explore attractions like Universal Studios Singapore and S.E.A. Aquarium. After a day of fun, head to Sentosaâ€™s Siloso Beach to relax or take part in water activities. In the evening, enjoy a Sentosa Island Night Show.', ' Sentosa Island,Universal Studios Singapore,S.E.A. Aquarium,Sentosa Siloso Beach,Sentosa Island Night Show', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-22'),
