(521, 66, 3, '7', 'Relaxing Farewell', 'Spend your final day at Singapore Botanic Gardens for a relaxing stroll, followed by a visit to the National Orchid Garden. In the afternoon, explore Raffles Place and do some last-minute shopping. End your trip with a farewell dinner at a top Singaporean restaurant before heading to the airport for departure.', 'Singapore Botanic Gardens,National Orchid Garden,Raffles Place', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-22'),
