(523, 67, 3, '2', 'Gardens by the Bay & Sentosa Adventure', 'Start your morning at the breathtaking Gardens by the Bay, where you can explore the futuristic Supertree Grove and the serene Cloud Forest. In the afternoon, make your way to Sentosa Island for some excitement and relaxation. Enjoy thrilling rides at Universal Studios Singapore or unwind on Siloso Beach. As evening falls, take in panoramic views from the Marina Bay Sands SkyPark before returning to Sentosa to witness the spectacular Wings of Time show by the sea.', 'Gardens by the Bay,Supertree Grove,Cloud Forest,Sentosa Island ,Universal Studios Singapore,Siloso Beach,Marina Bay Sands SkyPark, Wings of Time', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-23'),
