(526, 68, 3, '1', 'Arrival & Evening Stroll', 'Arrive in Singapore and take some time to settle in. In the evening, enjoy a peaceful stroll along Marina Bay, where you can admire the tranquil waters and illuminated skyline. Visit the Merlion Park to see the iconic statue and soak in the serene atmosphere as the city lights up.', 'Marina Bay,Merlion Park', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-23'),
(527, 68, 3, '2', 'Gardens by the Bay & ArtScience Museum', 'Start your morning with a visit to the lush Gardens by the Bay. Explore the calming Flower Dome and the mist-filled Cloud Forest. Spend your afternoon at the ArtScience Museum, where you can enjoy quiet reflection as you explore the serene exhibits. End your day with a gentle walk around the Supertree Grove and a relaxing evening by the bay.', 'Gardens by the Bay,Flower Dome,Cloud Forest,ArtScience Museum,Supertree Grove', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-23'),
