(531, 69, 3, '1', 'Arrival & Marina Bay Exploration', 'Arrive in Singapore and take the afternoon to settle in. Begin your journey with an evening stroll along Marina Bay, enjoying the stunning views of the skyline. Visit Merlion Park to see the iconic Merlion statue, and end your evening with the mesmerizing Spectra Light & Water Show at Marina Bay Sands.', 'Marina Bay,Merlion Park,Spectra Light & Water Show', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-23'),
