(1058, 137, 195, '5', 'Louvre Museum & Versailles Day Trip', 'Spend the morning exploring the world-renowned Louvre Museum, home to masterpieces like the Mona Lisa and the Venus de Milo. After your visit, take a short trip to the opulent Palace of Versailles. Tour the extravagant State Apartments, the breathtaking Hall of Mirrors, and the expansive Versailles Gardens. Return to Paris in the evening for a leisurely stroll along the Champs-Ã‰lysÃ©es and a view of the illuminated Arc de Triomphe.', 'Louvre Museum, Palace of Versailles, State Apartments, Hall of Mirrors, Versailles Gardens, Champs-Ã‰lysÃ©es, Arc de Triomphe', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-29'),
(1059, 137, 130, '6', 'Travel to Nice & Promenade des Anglais', 'Bid farewell to Paris as you travel to Nice, the jewel of the French Riviera. Upon arrival, check into your hotel and take a relaxing stroll along the famous Promenade des Anglais, a picturesque walkway along the Mediterranean coast. Enjoy the vibrant atmosphere and the beautiful sea views. In the evening, dine at a seaside restaurant, savoring the flavors of Mediterranean cuisine.', 'Promenade des Anglais', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-29'),
(1060, 137, 130, '7', 'Exploring Nice & Day Trip to Monaco', 'Spend the morning exploring the charming Old Town (Vieux Nice), with its colorful buildings, narrow streets, and lively markets. Visit the Cours Saleya Market, known for its fresh flowers and local produce. In the afternoon, take a short trip to the glamorous principality of Monaco. Explore the Monte Carlo Casino, the Prince\'s Palace, and the beautiful Monaco Harbor. Return to Nice in the evening to enjoy the local nightlife.', 'Old Town (Vieux Nice), Cours Saleya Market, Monaco, Monte Carlo Casino, Prince\'s Palace, Monaco Harbor', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-29'),
(1061, 137, 0, '8', 'Relaxation & Departure', 'On your final day, relax on one of Nice\'s beautiful beaches or visit the Matisse Museum to see works by the famous artist who called Nice his home. If time permits, take a leisurely walk through the Parc de la Colline du ChÃ¢teau for stunning views of Nice and the Mediterranean. Depending on your flight schedule, enjoy some last-minute shopping in the city center before heading to the airport for your departure, taking with you unforgettable memories of your journey through Zurich, Paris, and Nice.', '', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-29'),
