(1063, 138, 282, '2', 'Victoria & Morne Seychellois National Park', 'Start your day with a visit to Victoria, the charming capital of Seychelles. Explore the bustling Sir Selwyn Clarke Market, where you can find fresh produce, local spices, and souvenirs. Visit the Victoria Clock Tower, a replica of Londonâ€™s Big Ben, and the Botanical Gardens, home to giant tortoises and exotic plants. In the afternoon, venture into the Morne Seychellois National Park for a hike. Discover the islandâ€™s lush interior, with trails leading to panoramic viewpoints overlooking the island and the surrounding ocean.', 'Victoria, Sir Selwyn Clarke Market, Victoria Clock Tower, Botanical Gardens, Morne Seychellois National Park', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-29'),
