(1065, 138, 282, '4', 'Marine National Park & Relaxation', 'Embark on a boat tour to the Sainte Anne Marine National Park, where you can snorkel in the vibrant coral reefs and see a variety of marine life. Explore the parkâ€™s islands, including Cerf Island and Moyenne Island, which are known for their pristine beaches and wildlife. After your marine adventure, return to MahÃ© for a relaxing afternoon on the beach. Consider a spa treatment at your resort or a peaceful walk along the coastline.', 'Sainte Anne Marine National Park, Cerf Island, Moyenne Island', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-29'),
