(1073, 140, 100, '1', 'Arrival in MahÃ© & Beau Vallon Beach', 'Welcome to Seychelles! After your arrival in MahÃ©, settle into your hotel and begin your tropical getaway with a visit to Beau Vallon Beach. This popular beach is known for its expansive white sands and calm, clear waters, perfect for swimming and relaxing. Take a leisurely stroll along the shore or try out some water activities like snorkeling or parasailing. End your day with a seafood dinner at a beachfront restaurant, soaking in the beautiful sunset views.', ' Beau Vallon Beach', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-29'),
(1074, 140, 282, '2', 'Discover Victoria & Morne Seychellois National Park', 'Start your day exploring Victoria, the charming capital of Seychelles. Visit the Sir Selwyn Clarke Market to experience the vibrant local culture, where you can find fresh produce, spices, and crafts. Explore the Victoria Clock Tower and the peaceful Botanical Gardens, home to giant tortoises and rare tropical plants. In the afternoon, venture into the Morne Seychellois National Park for a hike through lush forests, leading to stunning viewpoints with panoramic views over MahÃ© and the surrounding islands.', 'Victoria, Sir Selwyn Clarke Market, Victoria Clock Tower, Botanical Gardens, Morne Seychellois National Park', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-29'),
(1075, 140, 284, '3', 'Transfer to Praslin Island & VallÃ©e de Mai Nature Reserve', 'After breakfast, travel to Praslin Island via a short ferry ride or flight. Check into your hotel and head to the UNESCO World Heritage site, the VallÃ©e de Mai Nature Reserve. Walk among ancient coco de mer palms and keep an eye out for the rare black parrot. Later, relax at Anse Lazio, a world-famous beach renowned for its soft white sand and crystal-clear waters, perfect for swimming and snorkeling. Enjoy the serene beauty of this idyllic spot before returning to your hotel.', 'Praslin Island, VallÃ©e de Mai Nature Reserve, Anse Lazio', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-29'),
