(1154, 152, 140, '6', 'Relax in Bentota', 'Enjoy a day of relaxation and leisure in Bentota. Start with a visit to the Kosgoda Turtle Hatchery, where you can learn about sea turtle conservation and even release baby turtles into the ocean. Later, visit the Brief Garden, the beautifully landscaped estate of the famous Sri Lankan architect Geoffrey Bawa. Spend the rest of the day at your leisure, whether indulging in a spa treatment or taking a peaceful walk along the beach. In the evening, explore Bentotaâ€™s local markets or dine at a beachfront restaurant.', 'Kosgoda Turtle Hatchery, Brief Garden', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-29'),
(1155, 152, 141, '7', 'Explore Colombo', 'Travel to Colombo, Sri Lankaâ€™s vibrant capital city. Check into your hotel and begin exploring the cityâ€™s mix of modernity and tradition. Visit the Gangaramaya Temple, a significant Buddhist temple that blends different architectural styles. Continue to Independence Square and the Independence Memorial Hall, important landmarks commemorating Sri Lankaâ€™s independence. In the evening, take a stroll along the Galle Face Green and enjoy the sunset together. Conclude your day with a romantic dinner at one of Colomboâ€™s fine dining establishments.', 'Gangaramaya Temple, Independence Square, Independence Memorial Hall, Galle Face Green', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-29'),
(1156, 152, 141, '8', 'Explore Colombo and Departure', 'On your final day, explore more of Colomboâ€™s attractions before your departure. Visit the Colombo National Museum, which houses an extensive collection of artifacts and exhibits showcasing Sri Lankaâ€™s rich history. Then, head to Pettah Market for some last-minute shopping, where you can find spices, textiles, and local crafts. Depending on your flight time, relax at one of Colomboâ€™s stylish cafes or take a leisurely walk through the city. Transfer to the airport for your onward journey, cherishing the unforgettable memories of your romantic getaway in Sri Lanka.', 'Colombo National Museum,  Pettah Market ', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-29'),
(1157, 154, 149, '1', 'Arrival in Phuket and Evening at Patong Beach', 'Upon arrival in Phuket, you\'ll be greeted at the airport and transferred to your hotel, where you can unwind after your journey. Later, head to Patong Beach to immerse yourself in the lively atmosphere, enjoying street food and exploring the vibrant nightlife. Your first day ends with a comfortable stay in Phuket.', 'Patong Beach', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1158, 154, 39, '2', 'Discover the Highlights of Phuket', 'After a leisurely breakfast, set out to explore Phuket\'s most iconic landmarks. Visit the towering Big Buddha, offering panoramic views of the island, and continue to the serene Wat Chalong Temple. Stroll through Phuket Old Town, where charming Sino-Portuguese architecture meets quaint cafes and shops. In the afternoon, relax or take an optional visit to Karon Viewpoint or Kata Beach before retiring for the night in Phuket.', 'Big Buddha, Wat Chalong Temple, Phuket Old Town, Karon Viewpoint or Kata Beach', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1159, 154, 107, '3', 'Explore the Stunning Phi Phi Islands', 'Day three promises adventure with a full-day excursion to the breathtaking Phi Phi Islands. You\'ll have the opportunity to snorkel in the crystal-clear waters of Maya Bay, explore the mysterious Viking Cave, and bask in the beauty of Bamboo Island. A delightful beachfront lunch will be served before you return to Phuket in the evening, where you\'ll spend another night.', 'Phi Phi Islands, Maya Bay, Viking Cave, Bamboo Island', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1160, 154, 38, '4', 'Journey from Phuket to Krabi', 'After breakfast, leave Phuket behind and enjoy the scenic drive to Krabi. Once you arrive, check in at your hotel and spend the evening exploring Ao Nang Beach. This area is perfect for a relaxed stroll along the beach, shopping at local markets, and dining at a seaside restaurant, all while soaking in the tranquil Krabi atmosphere.', 'Ao Nang Beach', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1161, 154, 38, '5', 'Experience the Beauty of Krabiâ€™s Four Islands', 'Your fifth day in Krabi is dedicated to the famous Four Islands Tour. After breakfast, embark on a boat tour to discover the stunning beaches of Phra Nang Cave Beach, Chicken Island, Poda Island, and Tup Island. Whether you\'re snorkeling, swimming, or simply lounging on the beach, this day is all about enjoying the natural beauty of Krabi. A picnic lunch on one of the islands adds to the day\'s charm, and you\'ll return to your hotel for your final night in Krabi.', 'Four Islands Tour, Phra Nang Cave Beach, Chicken Island, Poda Island, Tup Island', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1162, 154, 0, '6', 'Departure', 'On your final day, enjoy a leisurely breakfast and a relaxed morning. Depending on your flight time, you may have some last-minute shopping or beach time before transferring to the airport for your departure, bringing your amazing Phuket and Krabi adventure to a close.', '', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1163, 155, 39, '1', 'Arrival in Phuket', 'Begin your journey by arriving in Phuket, where you\'ll be welcomed at the airport and transferred to your hotel. After settling in, take some time to explore the lively Patong Beach area, known for its vibrant nightlife, street markets, and delicious local cuisine. This evening is all about soaking in the energy of Phuket before heading back to your hotel for a restful night.', 'Patong Beach', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1164, 155, 39, '2', 'Discover Phuket\'s Treasures', 'After breakfast, embark on a tour of Phuketâ€™s most famous sights. Start with a visit to the iconic Big Buddha, perched atop Nakkerd Hill, offering breathtaking views of the island. Next, explore the spiritual Wat Chalong Temple, a significant religious site for locals. Continue your journey to Phuket Old Town, where you can wander through streets lined with Sino-Portuguese architecture, charming cafes, and boutique shops. Optionally, spend the afternoon relaxing at Kata Beach or Karon Viewpoint before returning to your hotel for the night.', ' Big Buddha, Wat Chalong Temple, Phuket Old Town, Kata Beach or Karon Viewpoint', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1165, 155, 107, '3', 'Full-Day Adventure to Phi Phi Islands', 'On the third day, set out early for a full-day excursion to the world-renowned Phi Phi Islands. Start with a boat ride to Maya Bay, famously featured in the movie \"The Beach,\" where you can swim and snorkel in crystal-clear waters. Visit the impressive Viking Cave and enjoy a relaxing time on the stunning Bamboo Island. A beachside lunch will be provided during the tour, allowing you to fully appreciate the idyllic surroundings. After a day of exploration, return to Phuket for an overnight stay.', 'Phi Phi Islands, Maya Bay, Viking Cave, Bamboo Island', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1166, 155, 38, '4', 'Transfer to Krabi and Explore Ao Nang', 'After breakfast, check out from your hotel in Phuket and head towards Krabi. Upon arrival, check into your hotel and take some time to unwind. In the evening, explore Ao Nang Beach, a beautiful stretch of coastline perfect for a leisurely stroll. The area is known for its vibrant atmosphere, with plenty of shops, cafes, and seaside restaurants. Enjoy the laid-back vibes of Krabi before returning to your hotel for the night.', 'Ao Nang Beach', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1167, 155, 38, '5', 'Discover Krabi\'s Four Islands', 'Day five is dedicated to exploring the best of Krabiâ€™s coastline with a Four Islands Tour. After breakfast, embark on a boat journey to visit Phra Nang Cave Beach, famous for its stunning limestone cliffs and crystal-clear waters. Continue to Chicken Island, named for its unique rock formation, and enjoy some snorkeling. Visit Poda Island for a beachside picnic lunch and wrap up the day with a visit to Tup Island, where you can walk across a sandbar connecting the islands at low tide. Return to your hotel in Krabi for your final night.', 'Four Islands Tour, Phra Nang Cave Beach, Chicken Island, Poda Island, Tup Island', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1168, 155, 0, '6', 'Departure', 'On your final day, enjoy a relaxed breakfast and some free time in the morning. Depending on your flight schedule, you may have the opportunity for last-minute shopping or one last visit to the beach. When itâ€™s time, transfer to the airport for your departure, concluding your magnificent island-hopping adventure through Krabi, Phuket, and Phi Phi Island.', '', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1169, 156, 40, '1', 'Arrival in Pattaya and Leisure', 'Your journey begins with your arrival in Pattaya, where youâ€™ll be greeted and transferred to your hotel. After settling in, take the rest of the day to relax and explore the surroundings at your own pace. You might want to stroll along Pattaya Beach or visit one of the nearby markets to get a taste of the local culture. Enjoy a leisurely evening and prepare for the exciting days ahead.', 'Pattaya Beach', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1170, 156, 203, '2', 'Coral Island Tour and Nong Nooch Village', 'After breakfast, embark on a thrilling Coral Island Tour. Take a speedboat ride to Koh Larn (Coral Island), where you can indulge in water activities like parasailing, snorkeling, and jet-skiing, or simply relax on the sandy beaches. Return to Pattaya for lunch and later, visit Nong Nooch Tropical Garden, a beautifully landscaped park showcasing traditional Thai culture, stunning gardens, and captivating cultural performances. Return to your hotel for an overnight stay.', 'Coral Island Tour, Koh Larn (Coral Island), Nong Nooch Tropical Garden', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1171, 156, 40, '3', 'Explore Pattayaâ€™s Attractions', 'On day three, explore some of Pattayaâ€™s most popular attractions. Begin with a visit to the Sanctuary of Truth, an intricately carved wooden structure that stands as a testament to Thai craftsmanship and spirituality. Next, visit the Pattaya Floating Market, where you can experience the vibrant market life and sample local delicacies. In the evening, enjoy the famous Alcazar Cabaret Show, known for its dazzling performances. Return to your hotel for a restful night.', 'Sanctuary of Truth, Pattaya Floating Market, Alcazar Cabaret Show', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1172, 156, 41, '4', 'Transfer to Bangkok and City Tour', 'After breakfast, check out from your Pattaya hotel and transfer to Bangkok. Upon arrival, embark on a half-day city tour to discover the highlights of Thailand\'s capital. Visit the Grand Palace, the former royal residence, and marvel at its intricate architecture and revered Emerald Buddha. Continue to Wat Pho, home to the majestic Reclining Buddha, and then explore Wat Arun (Temple of Dawn), known for its stunning riverside location. Conclude the day by checking into your Bangkok hotel.', 'Grand Palace, Emerald Buddha, Wat Pho, Wat Arun (Temple of Dawn)', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1173, 156, 41, '5', 'Discover Bangkokâ€™s Culture and Shopping', 'Begin your day with a visit to Jim Thompson House, a museum dedicated to the American businessman who helped revive the Thai silk industry. Then, explore Chatuchak Weekend Market (if your visit coincides with the weekend) or visit one of Bangkokâ€™s upscale shopping malls like Siam Paragon or MBK Center. In the evening, take a Chao Phraya River Dinner Cruise, where you can enjoy delicious Thai cuisine while admiring the illuminated city skyline. Return to your hotel for the night.', 'Jim Thompson House, Chatuchak Weekend Market, Siam Paragon or MBK Center, Chao Phraya River Dinner Cruise', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1174, 156, 0, '6', 'Departure', 'On your final day, enjoy breakfast and some free time for last-minute shopping or exploring. Depending on your flight schedule, you may visit Erawan Shrine or take a stroll through Lumphini Park. When it\'s time, you\'ll be transferred to the airport for your departure, bringing your ultimate Bangkok and Pattaya experience to a close.', '', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1175, 157, 38, '1', 'Arrival in Krabi and Relaxation', 'Your romantic journey begins in Krabi, where you\'ll be welcomed and transferred to your hotel. Spend the day relaxing after your journey. In the evening, take a leisurely stroll along Ao Nang Beach, enjoying the serene ambiance and the first sunset of your trip. Indulge in a romantic dinner at a seaside restaurant before returning to your hotel for a peaceful night.', 'Ao Nang Beach', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1176, 157, 38, '2', 'Krabi\'s Four Islands Tour', 'Start your day with a boat trip on the famous Four Islands Tour. Visit Phra Nang Cave Beach, known for its stunning limestone cliffs and crystal-clear waters. Continue to Chicken Island for snorkeling, and explore the pristine shores of Poda Island. Finish the tour at Tup Island, where you can walk across the sandbar at low tide, hand in hand. After a day of sun and sea, return to your hotel in Krabi for a romantic evening.', ' Four Islands Tour, Phra Nang Cave Beach, Chicken Island, Poda Island, Tup Island', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1177, 157, 38, '3', 'Explore Railay Beach and Hot Springs', 'On day three, visit the picturesque Railay Beach, accessible only by boat. Spend your time lounging on the soft sand or swimming in the turquoise waters. In the afternoon, visit the Emerald Pool and the Krabi Hot Springs for a rejuvenating experience in the midst of nature. Return to your hotel in Krabi for a cozy night.', 'Railay Beach, Emerald Pool, Krabi Hot Springs', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1178, 157, 39, '4', 'Transfer to Phuket and Sunset at Promthep Cape', 'After breakfast, check out from your hotel and transfer to Phuket. Upon arrival, check into your hotel and spend the afternoon at leisure. In the evening, visit Promthep Cape, one of the most romantic spots in Phuket, known for its breathtaking sunset views. Enjoy a private dinner at a cliffside restaurant before heading back to your hotel.', 'Promthep Cape', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1179, 157, 107, '5', 'Phi Phi Islands Romance', 'Embark on a romantic day trip to the Phi Phi Islands, starting with a visit to Maya Bay, the famous filming location of \"The Beach.\" Snorkel together in the crystal-clear waters and enjoy a private lunch on the beach. Continue to Bamboo Island for some quiet time on its secluded shores before returning to Phuket. End the day with a sunset cruise back to the mainland.', 'Phi Phi Islands, Maya Bay, Bamboo Island', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1180, 157, 39, '6', 'Romantic Day in Phuket', 'Spend the day exploring Phuket at your own pace. Visit the Big Buddha for panoramic views, or take a romantic walk through Phuket Old Town with its charming cafes and colorful buildings. In the evening, enjoy a romantic sunset dinner cruise around Phuket\'s coastline, complete with a gourmet meal and live music.', 'Big Buddha, Phuket Old Town', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1181, 157, 40, '7', ' Transfer to Pattaya and Explore', 'After breakfast, transfer from Phuket to Pattaya. Upon arrival, check into your hotel and spend some time relaxing. In the evening, visit the Sanctuary of Truth, a unique wooden structure that symbolizes love and faith. Afterward, take a romantic walk along Pattaya Beach and enjoy a seafood dinner by the sea before heading back to your hotel.', 'Sanctuary of Truth, Pattaya Beach', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1182, 157, 40, '8', 'Coral Island and Pattaya Nightlife', 'Take a day trip to Coral Island (Koh Larn), where you can relax on the beautiful beaches or engage in water activities. Have a picnic on the beach and enjoy the tranquil surroundings. Return to Pattaya in the evening, and experience the vibrant nightlife together by attending the Alcazar Cabaret Show or exploring the bustling Walking Street. End the night with a romantic dinner at a rooftop restaurant.', 'Coral Island (Koh Larn), Alcazar Cabaret Show, Walking Street', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1183, 157, 41, '9', ' Transfer to Bangkok and Departure', 'On your final day, transfer from Pattaya to Bangkok. If time permits, visit Jim Thompson House or take a romantic stroll through Lumphini Park. Depending on your flight schedule, enjoy some last-minute shopping at Siam Paragon or MBK Center. When it\'s time, transfer to the airport for your departure, concluding your romantic Thailand adventure.', 'Jim Thompson House, Lumphini Park, Siam Paragon or MBK Center', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1184, 161, 168, '1', ' Arrival in Kuala Lumpur and City Introduction', 'Upon arrival in Kuala Lumpur, you\'ll be welcomed and transferred to your hotel. After settling in, begin your journey with an introductory tour of the city. Visit the iconic Petronas Twin Towers, where you can marvel at the stunning cityscape from the sky bridge. Next, explore the bustling Bukit Bintang district, known for its vibrant shopping and dining options. Enjoy a delicious Malaysian dinner before returning to your hotel for a restful night.', 'Petronas Twin Towers, Bukit Bintang', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1185, 161, 168, '2', 'Cultural Exploration and Historical Landmarks', 'Start your day with a visit to Batu Caves, a Hindu temple set within limestone caves, famous for its towering golden statue of Lord Murugan and the 272 steps leading up to the temple. Afterward, explore Merdeka Square, where you can admire the colonial architecture and learn about Malaysia\'s history. Continue to the Sultan Abdul Samad Building and visit the Kuala Lumpur City Gallery. End the day with a stroll through Central Market, a cultural hub where you can shop for traditional crafts and souvenirs.', 'Batu Caves, Merdeka Square, Sultan Abdul Samad Building, Kuala Lumpur City Gallery, Central Market', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1186, 161, 204, '3', 'Day Trip to the Genting Highlands', 'On day three, take a day trip to the Genting Highlands, a popular hill resort located just an hour\'s drive from Kuala Lumpur. Enjoy the scenic cable car ride up to the resort, where you can explore attractions like Genting SkyWorlds Theme Park, the Chin Swee Caves Temple, and SkyAvenue Mall. Try your luck at the Genting Casino or enjoy the cool climate while taking in the breathtaking mountain views. Return to Kuala Lumpur in the evening for a relaxing night at your hotel.', 'Genting Highlands, Genting SkyWorlds Theme Park, Chin Swee Caves Temple, SkyAvenue Mall, Genting Casino', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1187, 161, 168, '4', 'Modern Kuala Lumpur and Shopping Extravaganza', 'After breakfast, visit the modern side of Kuala Lumpur by exploring KLCC Park, a beautifully landscaped park in the heart of the city. Next, head to Suria KLCC, a premier shopping mall located at the base of the Petronas Towers, where you can indulge in high-end shopping and gourmet dining. Continue your shopping spree at Pavilion Kuala Lumpur, another luxury mall in Bukit Bintang. In the evening, enjoy a spectacular view of the city from the KL Tower observation deck before heading back to your hotel.', 'KLCC Park, Suria KLCC, Pavilion Kuala Lumpur, KL Tower', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1188, 161, 0, '5', 'Departure', 'On your final day, enjoy breakfast and some free time to explore any last-minute sights or do some final shopping. Depending on your flight schedule, you might visit Thean Hou Temple, a beautiful Chinese temple known for its intricate architecture and serene gardens, or take a walk through Kuala Lumpur Bird Park, one of the world\'s largest free-flight aviaries. When it\'s time, you\'ll be transferred to the airport for your departure, concluding your joyful journey in Kuala Lumpur.', '', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1189, 162, 168, '1', 'Arrival in Kuala Lumpur', 'Arrive in Kuala Lumpur and transfer to your hotel. After checking in, start your exploration of the city by visiting the iconic Petronas Twin Towers. Enjoy panoramic views of Kuala Lumpur from the sky bridge and observation deck. Spend your evening in the bustling Bukit Bintang area, known for its vibrant street life, shopping, and dining options. Return to your hotel for a comfortable nightâ€™s rest.', 'Petronas Twin Towers, Bukit Bintang', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1190, 162, 169, '2', 'Kuala Lumpur City Tour and Transfer to Genting Highlands', 'Begin your day with a visit to Batu Caves, a major Hindu pilgrimage site set in limestone caves. Explore the impressive golden statue of Lord Murugan and climb the colorful 272 steps. Next, visit Merdeka Square to admire colonial architecture and historical landmarks such as the Sultan Abdul Samad Building. In the afternoon, transfer to Genting Highlands, a hill resort known for its cool climate and entertainment options. Check into your hotel and enjoy the evening exploring the Genting SkyWorlds Theme Park or SkyAvenue Mall.', 'Merdeka Square, Sultan Abdul Samad Building, Genting Highlands, Genting SkyWorlds Theme Park or SkyAvenue Mall', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1191, 162, 169, '3', 'Full Day at Genting Highlands', 'Spend the entire day enjoying the attractions at Genting Highlands. Start with a thrilling adventure at Genting SkyWorlds Theme Park, featuring a variety of rides and entertainment. Explore the Chin Swee Caves Temple, a beautiful and serene temple complex nestled in the mountains. If youâ€™re feeling lucky, try your hand at the Genting Casino. In the evening, you can explore more of the resortâ€™s shopping and dining options before heading back to your hotel.', 'Genting SkyWorlds Theme Park, Chin Swee Caves Temple, Genting Casino', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1192, 162, 170, '4', ' Transfer to Langkawi and Beach Relaxation', 'After breakfast, check out from your hotel and transfer to Langkawi. Upon arrival, check into your hotel and spend the day relaxing on Langkawiâ€™s beautiful beaches, such as Pantai Cenang or Pantai Tengah. Enjoy the warm tropical weather and clear blue waters. In the evening, explore the local night markets or enjoy a beachfront dinner at a local restaurant.', 'Pantai Cenang or Pantai Tengah', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1193, 162, 170, '5', 'Langkawi Island Tour and Departure', 'On your final day, embark on a Langkawi Island Tour. Visit key attractions such as the Langkawi Sky Bridge, which offers stunning views of the island and the surrounding landscape, and the Langkawi Cable Car for a breathtaking ride up to Gunung Mat Cincang. Explore Eagle Square and visit the Underwater World Langkawi if time permits. Depending on your flight schedule, you may have some last-minute shopping or beach time. Transfer to the airport for your departure, concluding your memorable Malaysia tour.', 'Langkawi Island Tour, Langkawi Sky Bridge, Langkawi Cable Car, Eagle Square, Underwater World Langkawi', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1194, 163, 168, '1', 'Arrival in Kuala Lumpur', 'Arrive in Kuala Lumpur and transfer to your hotel. After checking in, begin your exploration with a visit to the iconic Petronas Twin Towers. Enjoy stunning views of the city from the sky bridge and observation deck. Spend the evening in Bukit Bintang, a vibrant district known for its shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Enjoy dinner at a local restaurant and relax at your hotel.', 'Petronas Twin Towers, Bukit Bintang', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1195, 163, 3, '2', 'Kuala Lumpur City Tour and Transfer to Singapore', 'Start your day with a visit to the Batu Caves, a major Hindu pilgrimage site with impressive limestone caves and a towering statue of Lord Murugan. Next, explore Merdeka Square and visit the Sultan Abdul Samad Building. In the afternoon, check out from your hotel and transfer to Singapore. Arrive in Singapore and check into your hotel. Spend the evening exploring Marina Bay Sands and the Gardens by the Bay.', 'Batu Caves, Merdeka Square, Sultan Abdul Samad Building, Marina Bay Sands, Gardens by the Bay', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1196, 163, 3, '3', 'Singapore City Tour', 'After breakfast, embark on a city tour of Singapore. Visit Singapore Botanic Gardens, a UNESCO World Heritage site known for its lush greenery. Explore the Orchard Road shopping district, and enjoy a visit to Little India and Chinatown. In the afternoon, head to the Singapore Flyer for panoramic views of the city, and visit Raffles Hotel to experience its historic charm. Enjoy the evening at Sentosa Island, where you can explore attractions such as Universal Studios Singapore, S.E.A. Aquarium, or relax on Sentosa Beach.', ' Singapore Botanic Gardens,  Orchard Road, Little India, Chinatown, Singapore Flyer, Raffles Hotel, Sentosa Island, Universal Studios Singapore, S.E.A. Aquarium, Sentosa Beach', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1197, 163, 207, '4', 'Sentosa Island Adventure and Night Safari', 'Spend the day enjoying the attractions on Sentosa Island. Visit Universal Studios Singapore for thrilling rides and entertainment, or explore other attractions like S.E.A. Aquarium or Adventure Cove Waterpark. In the evening, experience the Night Safari, a unique wildlife park that offers a nocturnal adventure through various habitats. Return to your hotel in Singapore for a restful night.', 'Sentosa Island, Universal Studios Singapore, S.E.A. Aquarium or Adventure Cove Waterpar, Night Safari', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1198, 163, 168, '5', 'Return to Kuala Lumpur and Free Time', 'Check out from your Singapore hotel and transfer back to Kuala Lumpur. Upon arrival, check into your hotel and spend the rest of the day at leisure. You might choose to explore additional attractions in Kuala Lumpur such as the KL Tower, Petaling Street Market, or Central Market. Enjoy some free time for shopping or relaxing at your own pace.', 'KL Tower, Petaling Street Market, or Central Market', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30'),
(1199, 163, 0, '6', 'Departure from Kuala Lumpur', 'On your final day, enjoy breakfast and some last-minute shopping or sightseeing in Kuala Lumpur. Depending on your flight schedule, you can visit Thean Hou Temple or take a stroll through Lumpini Park. When itâ€™s time, transfer to the airport for your departure, concluding your memorable tour of Malaysia and Singapore.', '', '1', 'Shiv', '2024-08-30');
