(3, 'Singapore', 'Singapore, officially the Republic of Singapore, is an island country and city-state in maritime Southeast Asia.', 'Singapore.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', '', 'Singapore Tour Packages', ''),
(4, 'Dubai', 'Dubai is a city and emirate in the United Arab Emirates known for luxury shopping, ultramodern architecture and a lively nightlife scene.', 'Dubai.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', 'Best Dubai tour packages and experience the luxury and adventure of this vibrant city. Book your dream vacation now!', 'Dubai Tour Packages', 'Best Dubai tour packages and experience the luxury and adventure of this vibrant city. Book your dream vacation now!'),
(5, 'Switzerland', 'Switzerland is a mountainous Central European country, home to numerous lakes, villages and the high peaks of the Alps.', 'Switzerland.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', '', 'Switzerland Tour Packages', ''),
(6, 'Maldives', 'The Maldives, officially the Republic of Maldives, and historically known as the Maldive Islands, is a country and archipelagic state in South Asia in the Indian Ocean.', 'Maldives.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', '', 'Maldives Tour Packages', ''),
(7, 'New Zealand', 'New Zealand is an island country in the southwestern Pacific Ocean.', 'New Zealand.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', '', 'New Zealand Tour Package', ''),
(8, 'Nepal', 'Nepal, officially the Federal Democratic Republic of Nepal, is a landlocked country in South Asia. It is mainly situated in the Himalayas, but also includes parts of the Indo-Gangetic Plain. ', 'Nepal.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', '', 'Nepal Tour Packages', ''),
(9, 'Bhutan', 'Bhutan, a Buddhist kingdom on the Himalaya eastern edge, is known for its monasteries, fortresses (or dzongs) and dramatic landscapes that range from subtropical plains to steep mountains and valleys.', 'Bhutan.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', '', 'Bhutan Tour Packages', ''),
(10, 'Mauritius', 'Mauritius, an Indian Ocean island nation, is known for its beaches, lagoons and reefs. ', 'Mauritius.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', '', 'Mauritius Tour Packages', ''),
(11, 'Greece', 'Greece is a country in southeastern Europe with thousands of islands throughout the Aegean and Ionian seas. Influential in ancient times, it\'s often called the cradle of Western civilization.', 'Greece.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', '', 'Greece Tour Packages', ''),
(12, 'Indonesia', 'Indonesia, officially the Republic of Indonesia, is a country in Southeast Asia and Oceania between the Indian and Pacific oceans.', 'Indonesia.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', '', 'Indonesia Tour Packages', ''),
(13, 'Portugal', 'Portugal is a southern European country on the Iberian Peninsula, bordering Spain. ', 'Portugal.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', '', 'Portugal Tour Packages', ''),
(14, 'Spain', 'Spain, a country on Europe’s Iberian Peninsula, includes 17 autonomous regions with diverse geography and cultures.', 'Spain.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', '', 'Spain Tour Packages', ''),
(15, 'Italy', 'Italy, a European country with a long Mediterranean coastline, has left a powerful mark on Western culture and cuisine.', 'Italy.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', '', 'Italy Tour Packages', ''),
(16, 'Netharland', 'The Netherlands, a country in northwestern Europe, is known for a flat landscape of canals, tulip fields, windmills and cycling routes. ', 'Netherland.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', '', 'Netharland Tour Packages', ''),
(17, 'United Kingdom', 'The United Kingdom, made up of England, Scotland, Wales and Northern Ireland, is an island nation in northwestern Europe.', 'United Kingdom.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', 'The best of Europe with our carefully curated tour packages. Uncover the charm and history of Europe with our unforgettable journeys.', 'Europe Tour Packages', 'The best of Europe with our carefully curated tour packages. Uncover the charm and history of Europe with our unforgettable journeys.'),
(18, 'Hungary', 'Hungary is a landlocked country in Central Europe. Its capital, Budapest, is bisected by the Danube River. ', 'Hungary.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', '', 'Hungary Tour Packages', ''),
(19, 'Czech Republic', 'The Czech Republic, also known as Czechia, is a landlocked country in Central Europe.', 'Czech Republic.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', '', 'Czech Republic Tour Packages', ''),
(20, 'France', 'France, in Western Europe, encompasses medieval cities, alpine villages and Mediterranean beaches. ', 'France.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', '', 'France Tour Packages', ''),
(21, 'Seychelles', 'The Seychelles is an archipelago of 115 islands in the Indian Ocean, off East Africa.', 'Seychelles.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', '', 'Seychelles Tour Packages', ''),
(22, 'Australia', 'Australia, officially the Commonwealth of Australia, is a country comprising the mainland of the Australian continent, the island of Tasmania, and numerous smaller islands.', 'Australia.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', '', 'Australia Tour Packages', ''),
(23, 'Turkiye', 'Turkey, officially the Republic of Turkiye, is a country mainly in Anatolia in West Asia, with a smaller part called East Thrace in Southeast Europe.', 'Turkey.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', '', 'Turkiye Tour Packages', ''),
(24, 'Sri Lanka', 'Sri Lanka, historically known as Ceylon and officially the Democratic Socialist Republic of Sri Lanka, is an island country in South Asia.', 'Sri Lanka.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', '', 'Sri Lanka Tour Packages', ''),
(25, 'Belgium', 'Belgium, a country in Western Europe, is known for medieval towns, Renaissance architecture and as headquarters of the European Union and NATO. ', 'Belgium.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', '', 'Belgium Tour Packages', ''),
(26, 'Germany', 'Germany is a Western European country with a landscape of forests, rivers, mountain ranges and North Sea beaches.', 'Germany.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', '', 'Germany Tour Packages', ''),
(27, 'Austria', 'Austria, formally the Republic of Austria, is a landlocked country in Central Europe, lying in the Eastern Alps.', 'Austria.avif', '1', 'Harshit Gupta', '2024-07-26', '', 'Austria Tour Packages', ''),
(28, 'Thailand', 'Thailand is a Southeast Asian country. It\'s known for tropical beaches, opulent royal palaces, ancient ruins and ornate temples displaying figures of Buddha.', 'Thailand.avif', '1', 'shiv', '2024-08-06', '', 'Thailand Tour Packages', 'Discover the beauty of Thailand with our exclusive tour packages. Explore stunning beaches, vibrant cities, and rich cultural heritage. Book now!'),
(31, 'Malaysia', 'Malaysia is a Southeast Asian country occupying parts of the Malay Peninsula and the island of Borneo. Its known for its beaches, rainforests and mix of Malay, Chinese, Indian and European cultural influences.', 'Malaysia.avif', '1', 'harshit gupta', '2024-08-22', '', 'Malaysia Tour Packages', ''),
(32, 'cambodia', 'Cambodia is a Southeast Asian nation whose landscape spans low-lying plains, the Mekong Delta, mountains and Gulf of Thailand coastline. Phnom Penh, its capital, is home to the art deco Central Market, glittering Royal Palace and the National Museum histo', 'daniel-lienert-LAI8am-RdVM-unsplash.jpg', '1', 'shiv', '2024-08-22', '', 'cambodia Tour Packages', '');
