(79, 12, 'Yogyakarta Special Region', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-07-05', 'The Yogyakarta Special Region, often known as Jogja, is a centre of Javanese culture, drawing tourists with its allure both historically and aesthetically. Notable features of the region are its rich traditions, its old temples, such as Prambanan and Borobudur, and its lively arts scene.', 'Yogyakarta Special Region (3).jpg', '', 'Yogyakarta Special Region Tour Packages', ''),
