(86, 15, 'Tuscany', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-07-05', 'Tuscany, in central Italy, is renowned for its gently undulating hills covered in olive groves and vineyards. It also boasts historic cities like Florence and Siena that showcase Renaissance art and architecture, providing visitors with a classic Italian experience of wine, art, and beautiful scenery.', 'Tuscany.jpg', '', 'Tuscany Tour Packages', ''),
