(88, 15, 'Roma provincia', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-07-05', 'Encompassing mediaeval cities, attractive countryside, and archaeological sites like Ostia Antica and Tivoli\'s Villa d\'Este, the province of Rome, which surrounds the city of Rome in the Lazio region of Italy, offers a unique combination of ancient history, natural beauty, and cultural richness.', 'jack-ward-rknrvCrfS1k-unsplash.jpg', '', 'Roma provincia Tour Packages', ''),
(89, 15, 'Venice', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-07-05', 'Built on a network of canals, Venice, Italy, is a unique city known for its breathtaking architecture, iconic sites like the Doge\'s Palace and St. Mark\'s Basilica, and romantic gondola rides. This charming city, nestled against a gorgeous aquatic setting, provides a unique fusion of art, culture, and history.', 'venice.jpg', '', 'Venice Tour Packages', ''),
(90, 16, 'Rotterdam', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-07-08', 'The second-biggest city in the Netherlands, Rotterdam, is well-known for its contemporary architecture, thriving arts and culture, and largest port in Europe. It provides a fusion of cutting-edge design and extensive marine heritage.', 'netherlands (2).jpg', '', 'Rotterdam Tour Packages', ''),
(92, 17, 'Edinburgh', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-07-08', 'Scotland\'s capital, Edinburgh, combines magnificent Georgian architecture with a touch of mediaeval charm. It is well-known for its famous castle, which is built on an old volcanic rock and provides sweeping city views.', 'Edinburgh, Scotland.jpg', '', 'Edinburgh Tour Packages', ''),
(93, 18, 'Budapest', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-07-08', 'Hungary\'s capital, Budapest, is located on either side of the Danube River and is well-known for its exquisite architecture, which combines Art Nouveau, Baroque, and Gothic design elements. It\'s well-known for its thermal springs and thriving arts community, and attractions like Buda Castle provide expansive vistas of the city.', 'Budapest.jpg', '', '', ''),
(94, 18, 'Eger', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-07-08', 'Hungary\'s Eger is renowned for its picturesque wine area, home to the world-famous Bull\'s Blood wine, and its ancient beauty, which is exemplified by the magnificent Eger Castle.', 'Eger (2).jpg', '', 'Eger Tour Packages', ''),
(95, 20, 'Prague', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-07-08', 'The Czech Republic\'s capital, Prague, is renowned for its breathtaking mediaeval architecture, thriving arts and culture, and iconic sites including Prague Castle and Charles Bridge. The city\'s renowned Astronomical Clock and cobblestone streets can be seen in its charming old town.', 'Prague.jpg', '', 'Prague Tour Packages', ''),
(97, 19, 'Karlovy Vary', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-07-08', 'The Czech resort town of Karlovy Vary is well-known for both its exquisite architecture and healing hot springs. It boasts lovely gardens and picturesque views in addition to being the site of the esteemed International Film Festival.\r\n', 'Karlovy Vary.jpg', '', 'Karlovy Vary Tour Packages', ''),
(98, 20, 'Paris', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-07-08', 'Renowned for its abundant culture and gastronomy, France is home to renowned structures like the Eiffel Tower and ancient locations like the Louvre Museum. Its many regions draw millions of tourists annually with everything from vibrant cities to breathtaking countryside.', 'Paris (4).jpg', '', '', ''),
