(100, 21, 'Mahe Island', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-07-09', 'The 115-island Seychelles archipelago in the Indian Ocean is well-known for its immaculate white sand beaches, glistening oceans, and abundant marine life. These attributes have made it a sought-after location for luxury and ecotourism travel. It provides private island retreats with luxuriant tropical scenery and distinctive Creole culture.', 'seychelles.jpg', '', '', ''),
(101, 21, 'Praslin Island', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-07-09', 'Renowned for its breathtaking beaches such as Anse Lazio and the UNESCO-designated VallÃ©e de Mai Nature Reserve, Praslin Island is the second largest island in the Seychelles. The island is a tropical wonderland with a variety of uncommon plants and animals, such as the Coco de Mer palm.', 'Praslin Island.avif', '', 'Praslin Island Tour Packages', ''),
(102, 22, 'Sydney', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-07-09', 'The largest city in Australia is Sydney, located in New South Wales. It is well-known for its breathtaking coastline beaches, lively culture, and famous buildings like the Sydney Opera House and Harbour Bridge. It offers a variety of outdoor, culinary, and shopping activities while fusing modernism with a deep colonial past.', 'Sydney, New South Wales.avif', '', '', ''),
(104, 22, 'Queensland', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-07-09', 'The world\'s biggest coral reef system, the Great Barrier Reef is located off the coast of Queensland, Australia, and is well-known for its colourful coral formations and diverse marine life. It is a UNESCO World Heritage site that stretches over 2,300 kilometres and attracts tourists for eco-tours, diving, and snorkelling.', 'Great Barrier Reef, Queensland.jpg', '', 'Queensland Tour Packages', ''),
(105, 2, 'Ha Long', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-07-10', 'Háº¡ Long, a city on Vietnamâ€™s northern coast, is a jumping-off point for Háº¡ Long Bay, a broad inlet of dramatic, often mist-covered limestone islands. ', '', '', 'Ha Long Tour Packages', ''),
(106, 32, 'Siem Reap', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-07-10', 'Siem Reap is the second-largest city of Cambodia, as well as the capital and largest city of Siem Reap Province in northwestern Cambodia.', '', '', 'Siem Reap Tour Packages', ''),
(107, 3, 'Phi Phi Island', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-07-10', 'The Phi Phi Islands are an island group in Thailand between the large island of Phuket and the Straits of Malacca coast of Thailand.The Phi Phi Islands are an island group in Thailand between the large island of Phuket and the Straits of Malacca coast of Thailand.', '', '', 'Phi Phi Island Tour Packages', ''),
