(136, 23, 'Cappadocia', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-07-19', 'Cappadocia, a semi-arid region in central Turkey, is known for its distinctive â€œfairy chimneys,â€ tall, cone-shaped rock formations clustered in Monks Valley, GÃ¶reme and elsewhere.', 'Cappadocia.jpg', '', 'Cappadocia Tour Packages', ''),
