(139, 24, 'Nuwara Eliya', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-07-19', 'Nuwara Eliya is a city in the tea country hills of central Sri Lanka. The naturally landscaped Hakgala Botanical Gardens displays roses and tree ferns, and shelters monkeys and blue magpies.', 'Nuwara Eliya.jpg', '', 'Nuwara Eliya Tour Packages', ''),
(140, 24, 'Bentota', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-07-19', 'Bentota is a resort town on Sri Lankaâ€™s southwest coast. Its long Bentota Beach stretches north, where it becomes a sandy strip known as Paradise Island, parallel to Bentota Lagoon.', 'Bentota.jpg', '', 'Bentota Tour Packages', ''),
