(149, 15, 'Amalfi', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-08-06', 'Amalfi is a town in a dramatic natural setting below steep cliffs on Italyâ€™s southwest coast', 'amalfi.webp', '', 'Amalfi Tour Packages', ''),
(150, 15, 'Arezzo', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-08-06', 'Arezzo is a city in eastern Tuscany, Italy. The hilltop Arezzo Cathedral features painted vaulted ceilings and a 15th-century fresco of Mary Magdalene by Piero della Francesca.', 'Arezzo.jpg', '', 'Arezzo Tour Packages', ''),
(151, 15, 'Ferrara ', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-08-06', 'Ferrara is a city in Italyâ€™s Emilia-Romagna region. Itâ€™s known for the buildings erected by its Renaissance rulers, the Este family. These include the moated Este Castle, with its lavish private chambers. ', 'Ferrara.jpg', '', 'Ferrara Tour Packages', ''),
(152, 15, 'Vicenza ', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '0000-00-00', 'Vicenza is a city in the Veneto region of northeast Italy. Itâ€™s known for the elegant buildings designed by the 16th-century architect Andrea Palladio.', 'Vicenza.avif', '', 'Vicenza Tour Packages', ''),
(153, 20, 'Chantilly ', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-08-06', 'Chantilly, residential town and tourist centre, Oise dÃ©partement, Hauts-de-France rÃ©gion, northern France, 26 miles (42 km) north of Paris by road.', 'Chantilly.jpg', '', 'Chantilly Tour Packages', ''),
(154, 23, 'Antalya', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-08-06', 'Antalya is a Turkish resort city with a yacht-filled Old Harbor and beaches flanked by large hotels. It\'s a gateway to Turkey\'s southern Mediterranean region, known as the Turquoise Coast for its blue waters.', 'Antalya.jpg', '', 'Antalya Tour Packages', ''),
(155, 0, 'lle aux Cerfs', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-08-07', 'lle aux Cerfs is a privately owned island near the east coast of Mauritius in the Flacq District. ', 'lle aux Cerfs.png', '', 'lle aux Cerfs Tour Packages', ''),
(156, 10, 'North Tour ', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-08-07', 'The Mauritius North Tour offers an exciting exploration of the island\'s vibrant northern region. This tour includes visits to charming locales like Grand Bay, bustling markets, and the serene Pamplemousses Botanical Garden. Travelers can also enjoy the stunning beaches, cultural sites, and lively nightlife, ensuring a comprehensive and memorable experience of Mauritius\'s northern charm.', 'North Tour.webp', '', 'North Tour Packages', ''),
(157, 1, 'Arunachal pradesh', 1, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-08-21', 'Arunachal Pradesh is a state in northeast India. It was formed from the North-East Frontier Agency region, and India declared it as a state on 20 February 1987. Itanagar is its capital and largest town. It borders the Indian states of Assam and Nagaland to the south.', 'sohan-rayguru-8pg0LoPoGEo-unsplash.jpg', '', 'Arunachal pradesh Tour Packages', ''),
(158, 1, 'Assam', 1, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-08-21', 'Assam is a state in northeastern India known for its wildlife, archeological sites and tea plantations. In the west, Guwahati, Assamâ€™s largest city, features silk bazaars and the hilltop Kamakhya Temple. Umananda Temple sits on Peacock Island in the Brahmaputra river. The state capital, Dispur, is a suburb of Guwahati. The ancient pilgrimage site of Hajo and Madan Kamdev, the ruins of a temple complex, lie nearby.', 'amit-ranjan-mhJODzwzCtg-unsplash.jpg', '', 'Assam Tour Packages', ''),
(159, 1, 'Manipur', 1, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-08-21', 'Manipur is a state in northeast India, with the city of Imphal as its capital. It is bounded by the Indian states of Nagaland to the north, Mizoram to the south and Assam to the west. It also borders two regions of Myanmar, Sagaing Region to the east and Chin State to the south.', 'leeder-bose-dxuFdu0vAqE-unsplash.jpg', '', 'Manipur Tour Packages', ''),
(160, 1, 'Meghalaya', 1, 1, 0, '1', '', '2024-08-21', 'Meghalaya is a state in northeast India. Meghalaya was formed on 21 January 1972 by carving out two districts from the state of Assam: the United Khasi Hills and Jaintia Hills and the Garo Hills.', 'bhuban-narzari-KjW3MKgGpQY-unsplash.jpg', '', 'Meghalaya Tour Packages', ''),
(161, 1, 'Mizoram', 1, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-08-21', 'Mizoram is a state in northeastern India, with Aizawl as its seat of government and largest city.', 'digilife-siaha-2cM78THYc4w-unsplash.jpg', '', 'Mizoram Tour Packages', ''),
(162, 1, 'Nagaland', 1, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-08-21', 'Nagaland is a mountainous state in northeast India, bordering Myanmar. It\'s home to diverse indigenous tribes, with festivals and markets celebrating the different tribes\' culture. Its capital city of Kohima suffered heavy fighting in World War II, commemorated by memorials at the Kohima War Cemetery. ', 'vipin-joseph-FOqtsX9Ra_M-unsplash.jpg', '', 'Nagaland Tour Packages', ''),
(163, 1, 'Tripura', 1, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-08-21', 'Tripura is a hilly state in northeast India, bordered on 3 sides by Bangladesh, and home to a diverse mix of tribal cultures and religious groups. In the capital Agartala, the imposing Ujjayanta Palace is set among Mughal gardens, and Gedu Miaâ€™s Mosque has white marble domes and towers. South of the city, Neermahal summer palace sits in the middle of Lake Rudrasagar and blends Hindu and Islamic architectural styles.', 'sourav-debnath-jQD7SPGj4Ug-unsplash.jpg', '', 'Tripura Tour Packages', ''),
(166, 1, 'Spiti Valley', 0, 1, 0, '1', '', '2024-08-21', 'Spiti is a high-altitude region of the Himalayas, located in the north-eastern part of the northern Indian state of Himachal Pradesh. The name \"Spiti\" means \"The middle land\", i.e. the land between Tibet and India.', 'divjot-ratra-kFttVr9ULSY-unsplash.jpg', '', 'Spiti Valley Tour Packages', ''),
(168, 31, 'Kuala Lumpur', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-08-22', 'Kuala Lumpur is the capital of Malaysia. Its modern skyline is dominated by the 451m-tall Petronas Twin Towers, a pair of glass-and-steel-clad skyscrapers with Islamic motifs.', 'Kuala Lumpur.jpg', '', '', ''),
(169, 31, 'Genting Highlands', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-08-22', 'Genting Highlands is a hill station located on the peak of Mount Ulu Kali in the Titiwangsa Mountains, central Peninsular Malaysia', 'Genting Highlands.jpg', '', 'Genting Highlands Tour Packages', ''),
(170, 31, 'Langkawi', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-08-22', 'Langkawi is one of Malaysia\'s best kept secrets, basking in the glistening turquoise waters of the Andaman Sea.', 'langkawi.jpg', '', 'Langkawi Tour Packages', ''),
(171, 31, 'Penang ', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-08-22', 'Penang is a state in northwest Malaysia comprising mainland Seberang Perai and Penang Island.', 'Penang.avif', '', 'Penang Tour Packages', ''),
(172, 6, 'Maafushi Island', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-08-23', 'Maafushi is one of the inhabited islands of Kaafu Atoll and the leading Local Toursim Island of the Maldives. The islandâ€™s proximity to MalÃ© and its transport hubs has allowed Maafushi to become a popular destination for tourists visiting local islands.', 'matheen-faiz-p1bm8vIzTK0-unsplash.jpg', '', 'Maafushi Island Tour Packages', ''),
(173, 7, 'Mount cook', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-08-23', 'Aoraki / Mount Cook is the highest mountain in New Zealand. Its height, as of 2014, is listed as 3,724 metres. It sits in the Southern Alps, the mountain range that runs the length of the South Island. A popular tourist destination, it is also a favourite challenge for mountain climbers. ', 'athithan-vignakaran-AoC8JenCCPU-unsplash.jpg', '', 'Mount cook Tour Packages', ''),
(174, 8, 'Bhaktapur', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-08-23', 'Bhaktapur, known locally as Khwopa and historically called Bhadgaon, is a city in the east corner of the Kathmandu Valley in Nepal located about 13 kilometres from the capital city, Kathmandu. Bhaktapur is the smallest city of Nepal as well as the most densely populated.', 'kerensa-pickett-FazSKoumQCQ-unsplash.jpg', '', 'Bhaktapur Tour Packages', ''),
(175, 10, 'North Island', 0, 0, 0, '1', '', '2024-08-27', 'The North Island of Mauritius is a vibrant and scenic destination, known for its stunning beaches like Grand Baie and Pereybere, lively towns, and rich culture. Visitors can explore the picturesque Cap Malheureux with its iconic red-roofed church, relax on Mont Choisy Beach, or discover the island\'s history at the Pamplemousses Botanical Garden and Lâ€™Aventure du Sucre museum. The area offers a perfect blend of relaxation, adventure, and cultural experiences in a beautiful tropical setting.', 'michael-DXQB5D1njMY-unsplash.jpg', '', 'North Island Tour Packages', '');
